%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22We%20left%20Texas%20for%20a%20year%20in%20Spain.%20After%203%20countries%20and%203%20school%20systems%2C%20we%20found%20where%20we%20belong.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223264%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20wearing%20a%20bike%20helmet%20bike%20riding%20in%20Spain.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a01764dc9dd4cb81cda90c7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222448%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EVictor%20Trac%20left%20Texas%20to%20spend%20a%20year%20in%20Spain%20with%20his%20family%3B%20they%20ended%20up%20settling%20in%20a%20new%20US%20city.%3Cp%3EProvided%20by%20Victor%20Trac%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EVictor%20Trac%2C%20now%2045%2C%20grew%20up%20in%20South%20Carolina%20and%20spent%20a%20few%20years%20in%20Europe%20after%20college%20with%20his%20now-wife.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThey%20started%20a%20family%20in%20Austin%20before%20moving%20with%20their%20two%20kids%20to%20Spain%20and%20later%20New%20Zealand.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAfter%20traveling%20along%20the%20East%20Coast%20in%20search%20of%20the%20right%20place%20to%20live%2C%20they%20settled%20in%20Portland%2C%20Maine.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Victor%20Trac%2C%2045%2C%20a%20DevOps%20engineer%20and%20entrepreneur.%20His%20words%20have%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGrowing%20up%20in%20South%20Carolina%2C%20I%20was%20always%20into%20computers.%20In%20high%20school%2C%20I%20built%20and%20sold%20PCs%20to%20my%20friends%20and%20their%20parents%20and%20provided%20tech%20support%20before%20earning%20a%20degree%20in%20electrical%20engineering%20and%20math.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20college%2C%20my%20then-girlfriend%20Rebecca%20%E2%80%94%20now%20my%20wife%2C%20who%20I've%20known%20since%20elementary%20school%20%E2%80%94%20took%20a%20teaching%20job%20in%20France%2C%20and%20I%20followed.%20We%20later%20spent%20three%20years%20living%20in%20Germany%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fplanned-family-trip-europe-without-focusing-itinerary-kids-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etraveling%20around%20Europe%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20weekends.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%202008%2C%20we'd%20returned%20to%20the%20US%20and%20moved%20to%20Austin%20as%20its%20startup%20scene%20was%20taking%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFast-forward%2015%20years%2C%20and%20Austin%20was%20no%20longer%20the%20intimate%20city%20we%20first%20landed%20in.%20Our%20kids%20were%209%20and%2012%2C%20and%20we%20saw%20it%20as%20the%20perfect%20time%20for%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fadult-gap-year-quit-job-travel-the-world-career-pivot-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Egap-year%20adventure%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20also%20knew%20Texas%20wasn't%20where%20we%20wanted%20to%20stay%20long%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223360%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Spanish%20lessons%20with%20with%20a%20teacher%20in%20Vitoria-Gasteiz%2C%20Spain.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0178f4c9dd4cb81cda90ca%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222520%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20family%2C%20pictured%20with%20a%20tour%20guide%2C%20spent%20a%20year%20in%20the%20capital%20of%20Spain's%20Basque%20Country%3B%20the%20school%20didn't%20teach%20in%20Spanish.%3Cp%3EProvided%20by%20Victor%20Trac%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22211bb7d4-1195-4b04-be06-1f9a0aa388f5%5C%22%3EThe%20family%20abroad%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20our%20kids%20attended%20a%20dual-language%20elementary%20school%20and%20already%20spoke%20Spanish%2C%20we%20decided%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-from-us-to-spain-adult-gap-year-quit-jobs-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Espend%20a%20year%20in%20Spain%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20we%20moved%20to%20Vitoria-Gasteiz%2C%20the%20capital%20of%20Spain's%20Basque%20Country%2C%20and%20rented%20a%20furnished%20duplex%20in%20a%20walkable%20city%20framed%20by%20mountains.%20There%20was%20one%20twist%3A%20The%20school%20taught%20primarily%20in%20Basque%2C%20a%20language%20completely%20unrelated%20to%20Spanish.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20kids%20struggled%20at%20first%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20my%20daughter%2C%20who%20barely%20spoke%20when%20we%20arrived%20%E2%80%94%20but%20within%20three%20months%2C%20they'd%20both%20adjusted.%20Friendships%20formed%2C%20the%20language%20became%20easier%2C%20and%20the%20experience%20exceeded%20anything%20we'd%20hoped%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20spent%20mornings%20trail%20running%20in%20the%20mountains%2C%20afternoons%20working%20remotely%20with%20US%20clients%20and%20my%20team%2C%20and%20evenings%20having%20dinner%20with%20my%20family.%20Life%20felt%20slower%20and%20more%20intentional%20than%20it%20had%20in%20Austin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223343%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20family%20posing%20by%20the%20Dolomites%2C%20Italy.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0176d7e1443b8dc48e3bfc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222507%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20family%20rented%20a%20camper%20van%20and%20traveled%20around%20Europe.%3Cp%3EProvided%20by%20Victor%20Trac%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20school%20year%20ended%2C%20we%20rented%20a%20camper%20van%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famericans-tested-different-european-countries-deciding-where-to-move-portugal-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eroad-tripped%20across%20southern%20Europe%3C%2Fa%3E%20before%20visiting%20friends%20and%20family%20in%20Ireland.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20August%202024%2C%20we%20were%20back%20in%20the%20US%2C%20but%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-from-austin-texas-to-new-york-city-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAustin%20house%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20rented%20out%2C%20and%20we%20weren't%20ready%20to%20settle%20down%20again.%20My%20wife%20also%20wanted%20to%20live%20somewhere%20with%20four%20distinct%20seasons%2C%20something%20we'd%20never%20really%20had%20in%20Texas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225567990c-6469-4122-a778-0e1b133b738b%5C%22%3EWe%20embarked%20on%20a%20%26quot%3Bcity%20shopping%20tour%26quot%3B%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20spent%20months%20traveling%20the%20East%20Coast%2C%20renting%20Airbnbs%20and%20testing%20cities%20as%20potential%20homes%20while%20my%20wife%20homeschooled%20the%20kids%20and%20I%20worked%20remotely.%20By%20December%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-small-city-maine-from-sweden-europe-community-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EPortland%2C%20Maine%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20had%20emerged%20as%20the%20clear%20winner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20timing%20was%20tricky%20because%20it%20was%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20US%20school%20year%2C%20so%20we%20decided%20to%20spend%20the%20first%20half%20of%202025%20in%20New%20Zealand%2C%20where%20school-aged%20children%20can%20attend%20local%20schools%20for%20up%20to%20three%20months%20on%20visitor%20visas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20enrolled%20the%20kids%20in%20a%20school%20in%20Christchurch%20on%20the%20South%20Island%20and%20headed%20off.%20At%20the%20Sydney%20airport%2C%20though%2C%20we%20hit%20a%20snag%3A%20Because%20we%20only%20had%20one-way%20tickets%2C%20Air%20New%20Zealand%20required%20proof%20of%20onward%20travel.%20I%20ended%20up%20buying%20expensive%20refundable%20exit%20tickets%20on%20my%20phone%20before%20we%20could%20check%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Family%20in%20life%20jackets%20with%20New%20Zealand's%20Mount%20Cook%20National%20Park%20in%20the%20background.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a017a01c9dd4cb81cda90cb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThey%20enrolled%20the%20kids%20for%20a%20semester%20at%20a%20school%20in%20Christchurch%2C%20New%20Zealand.%3Cp%3EProvided%20by%20Victor%20Trac%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20kids%20completed%20a%20school%20term%20and%20we%20did%20another%20big%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvisit-new-zealand-first-time-mistakes-solo-trip-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eroad%20trip%20exploring%20New%20Zealand%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20spent%20my%20days%20playing%20tennis%2C%20and%20at%20one%20point%2C%20I%20even%20cycled%20the%20Alps-to-Ocean%20trail%20in%20three%20days%2C%20with%20a%20laptop%20in%20my%20backpack.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20heading%20to%20Maine%2C%20we%20also%20spent%20three%20weeks%20in%20Japan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d78a8f1d-8dae-442d-a878-f6d6986027e5%5C%22%3EReadjusting%20to%20life%20in%20the%20US%20came%20with%20its%20own%20surprises%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Spain%20and%20New%20Zealand%2C%20daily%20life%20felt%20more%20walkable%20and%20connected.%20Back%20in%20the%20US%2C%20we%20suddenly%20found%20ourselves%20driving%20almost%20everywhere%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cost%20of%20everyday%20life%20also%20shocked%20us.%20In%20northern%20Spain%2C%20I%20could%20grab%20an%20espresso%20and%20a%20fresh%20pincho%20at%20a%20neighborhood%20caf%C3%A9%20for%20a%20couple%20of%20euros.%20Back%20in%20the%20US%2C%20even%20a%20simple%20coffee-and-breakfast%20run%20felt%20expensive%2C%20especially%20once%20tipping%20was%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20experiences%20abroad%20also%20changed%20how%20I%20viewed%20everyday%20interactions.%20In%20New%20Zealand%2C%20I%20rented%20an%20expensive%20camera%20lens%20with%20nothing%20more%20than%20my%20name%20written%20on%20a%20piece%20of%20paper%20%E2%80%94%20no%20ID%20or%20deposit%20required.%20That%20level%20of%20trust%20left%20a%20lasting%20impression%20on%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e3a5d946-f924-4e8e-b9b7-c9d1497e7a50%5C%22%3EPeople%20ask%20about%20the%20biggest%20challenge%20of%20living%20abroad%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20honestly%20don't%20think%20there%20was%20on