okesperson%20declined%20to%20provide%20specific%20numbers%2C%20telling%20Business%20Insider%20that%20it%20is%20implementing%20%26quot%3Borganizational%20changes%26quot%3B%20to%20best%20position%20itself%20for%20future%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJensen's%20memo%20says%20the%20marketing%20team%20is%20reducing%20its%20paid%20media%20spending.%20While%20Jensen%20didn't%20give%20specific%20examples%2C%20paid%20media%20typically%20means%20paying%20for%20Google%20Ads%20or%20other%20platforms%20for%20promotion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELinkedIn%20plans%20to%20embrace%20unspecified%20%26quot%3BAI%20tools%20and%20workflows%26quot%3B%20to%20help%20staff%20get%20things%20done%20faster.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flinkedins-layoffs-come-with-operational-changes-memo-shows-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ELinkedIn's%20product%20organizations%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20also%20been%20affected%20by%20the%20layoffs%2C%20as%20they%20made%20changes%20to%20their%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20cuts%20put%20LinkedIn%20squarely%20in%20line%20with%20the%20long%20list%20of%20tech%20companies%20that%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftech-companies-layoff-announcements-sound-similar-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epushing%20staff%20to%20use%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20they%20reduce%20head%20count.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcisco-announces-4000-layoffs-ai-driven-business-shift-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECisco%20announced%3C%2Fa%3E%20an%20AI-driven%20restructuring%20on%20Wednesday%20affecting%20about%204%2C000%20roles.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcoinbase-layoffs-ai-brian-armstrong-job-cuts-letter-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECompanies%20like%20Coinbase%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fblock-lay-off-4000-employees-read-jack-dorseys-memo-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBlock%20also%20cited%20increased%20productivity%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20AI%20as%20part%20of%20the%20rationale%20for%20their%20own%20layoffs%20earlier%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flinkedin-enters-ai-training-market-challenges-startups-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ELinkedIn%20is%20investing%20in%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20other%20ways%2C%20too.%20It%20launched%20an%20%26quot%3BAI%20labor%20marketplace%26quot%3B%20where%20people%20can%20make%20money%20training%20AI%20chatbots%20to%20get%20better%20at%20everything%20from%20coding%20to%20nursing%20to%20finance%2C%20Business%20Insider%20previously%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERead%20the%20full%20memo%20Jensen%20sent%20out%20on%20Wednesday%20below%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3ETeam%2C%20I%20want%20to%20start%20by%20saying%20that%20this%20team%20is%20doing%20extraordinary%20work.%20You're%20pushing%20our%20brand%20into%20new%20creative%20territory%2C%20delivering%20results%20that%20drive%20business%20growth%2C%20and%20being%20recognized%20for%20that%20in%20the%20industry%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it's%20making%20a%20real%20impact.%20Thank%20you.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20we're%20operating%20in%20a%20moment%20that%20requires%20more%20focus%20and%20intentionality.%20Growth%20is%20more%20competitive%2C%20infrastructure%20costs%20continue%20to%20rise%20and%20AI%20is%20reshaping%20how%20work%20gets%20done.%20So%20we%20are%20at%20a%20point%20where%20our%20work%20is%20important%20and%20deeply%20valued%2C%20and%20we%20need%20to%20reduce%20costs%20in%20Marketing%20to%20ensure%20LinkedIn%20is%20positioned%20for%20the%20future%20we're%20building.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EWith%20this%20in%20mind%2C%20we're%20making%20some%20organizational%20changes%2C%20including%20reducing%20roles%20across%20our%20team.%20If%20your%20role%20is%20part%20of%20the%20reductions%2C%20or%20proposed%20reductions%20in%20EMEA%20and%20APAC%2C%20you%20will%20receive%20a%20calendar%20invite%20in%20the%20next%20hour%20titled%20'Attendance%20Required%3A%20Marketing%20Organizational%20Updates.'%20If%20you%20do%20not%20receive%20this%20exact%20invite%20your%20role%20is%20not%20part%20of%20the%20reductions%20or%20proposed%20reductions.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3ETo%20give%20you%20more%20context%2C%20our%20organizational%20changes%20are%20across%20three%20areas%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EFirst%2C%20sharpening%20our%20financial%20focus.%20In%20addition%20to%20the%20difficult%20role%20reductions%20we're%20announcing%20today%2C%20we're%20also%20reducing%20our%20paid%20media%20and%20program%20spend%2C%20while%20continuing%20to%20invest%20where%20we%20see%20the%20highest%20ROI.%20This%20is%20about%20being%20more%20intentional%20with%20our%20resources%2C%20and%20creating%20space%20to%20fund%20the%20work%20that%20moves%20the%20business%20the%20most.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3ESecond%2C%20focusing%20our%20investments%20on%20where%20we%20can%20grow%20and%20drive%20high%20ROI%20in%20FY27.%20That%20includes%20accelerating%20LMS%20growth%2C%20advancing%20our%20agentic%20hiring%20solutions%2C%20and%20building%20on%20strong%20momentum%20with%20Premium%20and%20Small%20Business%20offerings.%20We'll%20prioritize%20the%20consumer%20experiences%20that%20most%20directly%20drive%20engagement%20and%20revenue%2C%20concentrate%20our%20marketing%20investments%20in%20the%20US%20and%20UK%2C%20and%20maintain%20our%20market%20leadership%20in%20LSS%20as%20we%20continue%20to%20strengthen%20the%20product.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EThird%2C%20setting%20teams%20up%20for%20success.%20We're%20continuing%20to%20bring%20teams%20together%20that%20do%20similar%20work%20in%20our%20Creative%20CoE%2C%20our%20Scaled%20Solutions%20org%2C%20and%20Small%20Business%20Marketing.%20We'll%20also%20embrace%20new%20AI-enabled%20tools%20and%20workflows%20that%20allow%20our%20human%20creativity%20and%20judgment%20to%20go%20further%2C%20faster.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3ETo%20those%20leaving%20LinkedIn%2C%20thank%20you%20for%20the%20care%2C%20creativity%20and%20commitment%20you%20brought%20to%20our%20culture%20and%20brand.%20You've%20made%20a%20lasting%20impact%2C%20and%20we're%20deeply%20grateful.%20For%20those%20staying%2C%20please%20join%20me%20in%20supporting%20our%20departing%20colleagues%20as%20they%20navigate%20what's%20next.%20We'll%20come%20together%20tomorrow%20for%20an%20all%20Marketing%20team%20meeting%20where%20I'll%20provide%20more%20clarity%20and%20you'll%20have%20a%20chance%20to%20ask%20questions.%20You%20can%20learn%20more%20about%20the%20changes%20within%20each%20team%20on%20the%20Marketing%20Hub%20which%20will%20include%20links%20to%20updates%20that%20GBO%2C%20Product%2C%20and%20Engineering%20are%20sharing%20today%20as%20well.%20Your%20leaders%20will%20provide%20more%20context%20on%20what's%20happening%20on%20your%20team%20in%20meetings%20later%20this%20week.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EWhile%20I%20know%20that%20this%20level%20of%20change%20can%20bring%20a%20sense%20of%20uncertainty%2C%20it%20can%20also%20clarify%20our%20purpose.%20The%20world%20needs%20LinkedIn%20now%20more%20than%20ever%2C%20and%20while%20these%20are%20hard%20choices%20to%20make%2C%20they%20focus%20our%20work%20for%20our%20short%20and%20long-term%20impact.%20Please%20take%20the%20time%20you%20need%20to%20process%20this%20news%20and%20give%20one%20another%20space%20at%20this%20moment.%20Thank%20you%20for%20everything%20you%20do%20for%20LinkedIn%20and%20for%20one%20another.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EJessica%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHave%20a%20tip%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20via%20email%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Acrollet%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Ecrollet%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20or%20on