ing%20Machines%20Lab%2C%20during%20the%20Nvidia%20GTC%20conference%20in%20San%20Jose%2C%20California%2C%20US%2C%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20March%2018%2C%202026.%20Nvidia%20Corp.%20Chief%20Executive%20Officer%20Jensen%20Huang%20said%20the%20company%20is%20firing%20up%20manufacturing%20of%20H200%20AI%20accelerators%20for%20customers%20in%20China%2C%20a%20sign%20of%20progress%20in%20the%20chipmaker's%20effort%20to%20reenter%20the%20vital%20market.%20Photographer%3A%20David%20Paul%20Morris%2FBloomberg%20via%20Getty%20Images%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fbca21c9dd4cb81cda7ead%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222666%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJurors%20heard%20again%20a%20videotaped%20deposition%20by%20former%20OpenAI%20executive%20Mira%20Murati.%3Cp%3EBloomberg%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220f595fd8-48a2-467e-9d7f-1bee1da5d22d%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EOpenAI%20lawyers%20hit%20rewind%20on%20damning%20depos%20to%20make%20their%20case%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20Musk's%20lawyers%20played%20a%20series%20of%20videotaped%20depositions%20from%20former%20OpenAI%20board%20members%20and%20executives%20who%20complained%20about%20Altman%2C%20including%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-witness-testimony-hits-sam-altman-in-trial-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Bculture%20of%20lying%26quot%3B%20they%20say%20he%3C%2Fa%3E%20created%20at%20OpenAI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20OpenAI's%20lawyers%20hit%20play%20on%20some%20of%20the%20same%20tapes%20to%20make%20a%20different%20point%3A%20Those%20same%20people%20supported%20the%20ChatGPT%20maker's%20partnerships%20with%20Microsoft%2C%20which%20is%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20Musk's%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20realized%20this%20was%20the%20best%20path%20forward%20for%20building%20what%20OpenAI%20was%20deciding%20to%20build%2C%26quot%3B%20former%20board%20member%20%3Ca%20href%3D