d%20Wednesday%2C%20described%20a%20workplace%20inside%20Anthropic%20where%20AI%20systems%20increasingly%20handle%20the%20execution%20layer%20of%20knowledge%20work%20%E2%80%94%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsoftware-engineers-lessons-white-collar-works-ai-disruption-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esoftware%20engineering%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20financial%20reporting%20%E2%80%94%20while%20humans%20shift%20toward%20oversight%2C%20judgment%2C%20and%20strategy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20hired%20a%20lot%20more%20people%20because%20of%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Rao%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20sees%20Claude%20as%20a%20productivity%20%26quot%3Baccelerant.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20actually%20means%20that%20we%20can%20get%20a%20lot%20more%20done%2C%20and%20that%20even%20as%20we%20grow%20the%20team%2C%20those%20people%20are%20more%20productive%20as%20they%20come%20up%20the%20curve%20on%20how%20to%20use%20Claude%20within%20our%20company.%20And%20I%20think%20that's%20starting%20to%20be%20true%20across%20many%20companies%20as%20well.%20%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20comments%20offer%20a%20glimpse%20into%20how%20one%20of%20Silicon%20Valley's%20leading%20AI%20companies%20believes%20artificial%20intelligence%20will%20reshape%20white-collar%20jobs%3A%20not%20necessarily%20by%20eliminating%20workers%20outright%2C%20but%20by%20automating%20large%20portions%20of%20their%20day-to-day%20tasks%20and%20turning%20employees%20into%20supervisors%20of%20AI%20systems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20shift%20is%20already%20happening%20inside%20Anthropic%20itself%2C%20Rao%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B90%20plus%20percent%20of%20our%20code%20is%20actually%20written%20by%20Claude%20Code%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsneaky-rise-shadow-ai-workplace-claude-it-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAnthropic's%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%20coding%20product.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company's%20finance%20team%20is%20undergoing%20a%20similar%20transformation%2C%20Rao%20said.%20Anthropic%20now%20uses%20Claude%20to%20produce%20financial%20statements%2C%20while%20its%20monthly%20financial%20review%20process%20is%20%26quot%3B90%20to%2095%25%20ready%26quot%3B%20before%20humans%20step%20in%20to%20review%20and%20interpret%20the%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20used%20to%20take%20hours%20to%20produce%2C%26quot%3B%20Rao%20said%20of%20some%20internal%20reports%2C%20%26quot%3Bnow%20comes%20down%20to%2030%20minutes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERao%20argued%20that%20the%20productivity%20gains%20have%20allowed%20Anthropic%20employees%20to%20spend%20less%20time%20gathering%20information%20and%20more%20time%20making%20decisions%20about%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20of%20it%20as%2C%20you%20know%2C%20accentuating%20and%20accelerating%20the%20talent%20that%20we%20already%20have%2C%26quot%3B%20Rao%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20talk%20a%20lot%20about%20how%20talent%20density%20beats%20talent%20mass%2C%20and%20I%20think%20that's%20true%20here%20%E2%80%94%20like%2C%20we%20want%20the%20densest%20collection%20of%20AI%20research%20talent%2C%20and%20inference%20engineering%20talent.%20And%20that%2C%20enabled%20with%20the%20best%20models%2C%20we%20think%20is%20a%20really%20winning%20combination.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22981f3117-09b6-460a-b572-99edd5db9d85%5C%22%3EAI's%20effect%20on%20the%20workforce%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDetails%20about%20how%20Anthropic's%20staff%20use%20AI%20come%20as%20companies%20across%20industries%20race%20to%20integrate%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-ai-ceo-mustafa-suleyman-white-collar-tasks-automation-prediction-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etechnology%20in%20the%20workplace%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Some%20firms%20have%20pushed%20employees%20to%20adopt%20AI%20as%20automation%20capabilities%20improve%2C%20while%20others%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flist-companies-replacing-human-employees-with-ai-layoffs-workforce-reductions%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecut%20jobs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20citing%20new%20AI-driven%20efficiencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20shift%20has%20fueled%20a%20growing%20debate%20among%20economists%20and%20executives%20over%20whether%20AI%20will%20ultimately%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-job-market-labor-unemployment-jevons-paradox-apollo-torsten-slok-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ereplace%20white-collar%20workers%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20make%20them%20more%20productive.%20Some%20warn%20automation%20could%20eliminate%20jobs%20faster%20than%20new%20ones%20can%20be%20created%2C%20while%20others%20argue%20productivity%20gains%20could%20ultimately%20increase%20labor%20demand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20employees%20become%20more%20productive%20with%20AI%20assistance%2C%20Rao%20said%2C%20companies%20may%20actually%20expand%20hiring%20because%20%26quot%3Bthere's%20no%20shortage%20of%20work%20to%20do.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20Rao's%20description%20of%20the%20workplace%20inside%20Anthropic%20suggests%20the%20nature%20of%20white-collar%20work%20is%20already%20changing%20rapidly.%20He%20said%20employees%20increasingly%20oversee%20AI%20systems%20rather%20than%20completing%20tasks%20manually%2C%20while%20teams%20deploy%20%26quot%3Bfleets%20of%20agents%26quot%3B%20that%20work%20across%20projects%20simultaneously.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEveryone%20kind%20of%20becomes%20a%20manager%2C%26quot%3B%20Rao%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20implications%20of%20that%20and%20the%20productivity%20gain%20that%20can%20come%20from%20that%20%E2%80%94%20we're%20very%2C%20very%20early%20in%20that%2C%20but%20the%20potential%20for%20it%20is%20incredible.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-cfo-white-collar-jobs-changed-execution-oversight-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C