.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finsider-reviews-expertise-in-product-reviews%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELearn%20more%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223912%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Samsung%20Galaxy%20A37%20phone%20leaning%20on%20a%20wooden%20post%20outside.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a04b777abc4e9d88574937d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222933%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%2FAra%20Wagoner%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20popular%20phones%20in%20Samsung's%20smartphone%20portfolio%20aren't%20the%20uncannily%20thin%20Folds%20or%20the%20pen-touting%20Ultras%3B%20they%20are%20the%20Galaxy%20A-series%20phones%20that%20make%20up%20the%20bulk%20of%20Samsung's%20sales%20and%20rank%20among%20the%20best-selling%20phones%20in%20the%20world%20quarter%20after%20quarter.%20I%20expect%20the%20%3Ca%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15126427790pc-20%26h%3D83791fd152a7909ed9274fa36be6ae862fe06ac6cff9cd8df58e5ca2c2a9dc95%26postID%3D6a04aaa61a1c27f79ffe2538%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftech%252Fsamsung-galaxy-a37-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FSamsung-A37-Unlocked-Smartphone-Warranty%252Fdp%252FB0GMKXXTV1%252F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESamsung%20Galaxy%20A37%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20replace%20its%20A36%20predecessor%20in%20short%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20A-series%20of%20phones%20isn't%20aiming%20at%20feature-chasing%20power%20users%20who%20feel%20the%20need%20to%20upgrade%20every%20year%20or%20two%2C%20though.%20Instead%2C%20the%20series%20aims%20to%20provide%20a%20reliable%20device%20you'll%20be%20happy%20keeping%20for%20a%20few%20extra%20years%2C%20an%20affordable%20phone%20that%20looks%20a%20heck%20of%20a%20lot%20closer%20to%20its%20premium%20flagship%20siblings%20while%20making%20a%20few%20reasonable%20spec%20sacrifices%20under%20the%20hood.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20none%20of%20the%20changes%20between%20the%20new%20A37%20and%202025's%20A36%20are%20earth-shattering%2C%20even%20the%20most%20modest%20of%20iterative%20updates%20allows%20the%20A37%20to%20remain%20a%20worthwhile%20value%2C%20despite%20a%20%2450%20price%20increase.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20A37's%20cameras%20are%20largely%20unchanged%20outside%20a%20slight%20boost%20to%20the%20Nightography%20mode.%20Galaxy%20AI%20mostly%20consists%20of%20existing%20features%20(like%20Circle%20to%20Search)%20or%20is%20about%20a%20year%20behind%20the%20Pixel%20counterpart%20(Object%20Eraser%20and%20Suggested%20Edits).%20Still%2C%20it's%20hard%20to%20go%20wrong%20with%20a%20big%20screen%20bright%20enough%20to%20(mostly)%20read%20outside%2C%2045W%20fast%20charging%2C%20and%20six%20years%20of%20promised%20system%20and%20security%20updates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22935a7e66-982a-4f72-a331-f089309e5e45%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Design%5C%22%3EDesign%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Samsung%20Galaxy%20A37%20phone%20on%20a%20worn%20blue%20wooden%20table.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a04b4cdecd7cc1332baed58%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223072%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20familiar%20design%20now%20persists%20across%20almost%20all%20of%20Samsung's%20phones.%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%2FAra%20Wagoner%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20only%20does%20the%20Galaxy%20A37%20look%20nigh-on%20identical%20to%20the%20slightly%20more%20powerful%20Galaxy%20A57%2C%20it's%20identical%20to%20the%20rest%20of%20this%20year's%20and%20last%20year's%20A-series%3A%20a%20vertical%20camera%20bar%20%E2%80%94%20branded%20the%20Ambient%20Island%20by%20Samsung%20during%20the%20Galaxy%20S26%20series%20launch%20%E2%80%94%20in%20the%20top%20left%20corner%20of%20the%20backplate%2C%20power%20button%20under%20the%20volume%20rocker%20on%20the%20right%20side%20of%20the%20frame%2C%20bottom-mounted%20SIM%20tray%2C%20and%20screen%20bezels%20just%20asymmetrical%20enough%20to%20bug%20you%20if%20and%20when%20you%20notice%20them%20around%20the%20edges%20of%20the%20case%20you%20%3Cem%3Ewill%3C%2Fem%3E%20be%20putting%20on%20this%20phone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhy%20am%20I%20so%20confident%20you'll%20be%20using%20a%20case%3F%20Because%20like%20every%20phone%20with%20a%20vertical%2C%20non-centered%20camera%20bar%2C%20the%20Galaxy%20A37%20will%20teeter-totter%20if%20you%20try%20to%20use%20it%20flat%20on%20a%20table.%20If%20that%20isn't%20enough%2C%20the%20Gorilla%20Glass%20Victus%2B%20covering%20the%20back%20of%20this%20phone%20felt%20and%20looked%20like%20an%20inoculated%20petri%20dish%20after%20less%20than%20three%20days%20of%20full%20use.%20Before%20looking%20at%20the%20spec%20sheet%2C%20I%20didn't%20even%20think%20it%20was%20glass%3B%20I%20just%20thought%20it%20was%20plastic%20with%20a%20cheap%2C%20glossy%20finish.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222943%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rear%20of%20Samsung%20Galaxy%20A37%20phone%20with%20fingerprints%20showing%20on%20glass.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a04b3fa7c7e83f26041b576%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222207%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20grime%20pictured%20here%20only%20took%20half%20an%20hour%20of%20Pok%C3%A9mon%20Go%20to%20accumulate.%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%2FAra%20Wagoner%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Samsung%20touts%20the%20glossy%20mirror%20finish%20as%20a%20key%20design%20feature%20'that's%20made%20to%20be%20shown%20off'%2C%20but%20it%20falls%20victim%20to%20the%20same%20slippery%20curse%20as%20dozens%20of%20previous%20Galaxy%20phones.%20When%20it's%20clean%2C%20the%20phone%20turns%20into%20a%20bar%20of%20soap%20the%20second%20your%20hands%20are%20sweaty.%20Then%2C%20after%20a%20couple%20of%20days%2C%20dead%20skin%20cells%20and%20grease%20from%20your%20hands%20turn%20it%20into%20a%20smudgy%20mess.%20Most%20manufacturers%20left%20glossy%20and%20mirror-finish%20phones%20behind%20for%20frosted%2C%20brushed%2C%20or%20matte%20finishes%20with%20grippier%20textures%20and%20cleaner%20aesthetics%2C%20and%20it's%20an%20utter%20shame%20we%20can't%20see%20that%20with%20one%20of%20Samsung's%20most%20popular%20models.%20But%20all%20a%20minor%20concern%20if%20you're%20putting%20a%20case%20on%20anyway%2C%20in%20all%20fairness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223691%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Side%20view%20of%20the%20Samsung%20Galaxy%20A37%20and%20its%20buttons%20on%20a%20red%20table.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a04b37c58810e27922ad4d6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222767%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20metallic%20paint%20effect%20on%20the%20frame%20is%20grippier%20and%20less%20prone%20to%20fingerprints%20than%20the%20back.%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%2FAra%20Wagoner%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20'ceramic%20glaze'%20on%20the%20plastic%20frame%2C%20thankfully%2C%20is%20not%20slippery%2C%20and%20the%20brushed%20matte%20finish%20won't%20show%20every%20fingerprint%20or%20micro-scratch%20the%20way%20a%20mirror-finish%20frame%20does.%20I%20appreciate%20how%20it%20slightly%20bumps%20out%20around%20the%20buttons%20to%20help%20you%20feel%20how%20far%20up%20or%20down%20your%20grip%20is%20when%20you're%20grabbing%20it%20blind%2C%20especially%20since%20the%20front%20and%20back%20of%20this%20phone%20are%20identical%20Victus%2B%20glass.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20smooth%20front%20glass%20made%20the%206.7-inch%20touchscreen%20on%20the%20A37%20a%20breeze%20to%20scroll%2C%20stream%2C%20and%20drag%20my%20puzzle%20pieces%20into%20place%2C%20and%20it%20got%20plenty%20bright%20for%20indoor%20use.%20Outdoors%20is%20a%20bit%20trickier%3A%20most%20of%20the%20time%2C%20the%20screen%20was%20bright%20enough%20to%20read%20effortlessly%2C%20but%20when%20the%20phone%20heated%20up%20after%20a%20photo%20safari%20around%20Disney's%20Animal%20Kingdom%20or%20while%20playing%20Pok%C3%A9mon%20Go%2C%20the%20screen%20dimmed%20and%20became%20difficult%20to%20read%20in%20direct%20sunlight%20(as%20shown%20in%20the%20photo%20below).%20This%20throttling%20is%20a%20safety%20measure%20to%20prevent%20burn-in%20on%20the%20AMOLED%20panel%2C%20and%20it%20doesn't%20take%20long%20for%20things%20to%20cool%20back%20down%20and%20brighten%20back%20up%20once%20you%20reach%20the%20shade.%20However%2C%20this%20could%20be%20a%20dealbreaker%20for%20those%20who%20work%20outdoors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Side-by-side%20images%20of%20screen%20displays%20of%20Samsung%20Galaxy%20A37.%20The%20left%20screen%20is%20considerably%20brighter%20than%20the%20one%20on%20the%20right.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a04af6c95396a3b6e41804e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20dimming%20during%20throttling%2C%20as%20shown%20on%20the%20right%2C%20makes%20for%20a%20dull%20viewing%20experience%20in%20bright%20sunlight.%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%2FAra%20Wagoner%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20PWM%20sensitive%20%E2%80%94%20or%20prone%20to%20eye%20strain%20headaches%20%E2%80%94%20the%20120Hz%20refresh%20rate%20isn't%20high%20enough%20to%20avoid%20flicker%20entirely%2C%20%3Cem%3Ebut%3C%2Fem%3E%20Samsung%20has%20obtained%20an%20Eye%20Care%20Certification%20by%20SGS%20for%20the%20blue-blocking%20Eye%20Comfort%20Shield%2C%20which%20gets%20about%20twice%20as%20strong%20as%20the%20Pixel%2010%20series%20I%20compared%20it%20to.%20With%20this%20extra-yellow%20filter%20enabled%2C%20I%20didn't%20experience%20much%20strain%20with%20the%20A37%2C%20except%20when%20I%20had%20to%20turn%20it%20off%20for%20my%20review%20photos.%20My%20sensitivity%20is%20on%20the%20lower%20end%20of%20the%20spectrum%2C%20though%2C%20so%20your%20mileage%20may%20vary.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20fingerprint%20sensor%20sits%20quite%20low%20under%20the%20screen%2C%20meaning%20it%20doesn't%20overlap%20the%20number%20pad%20on%20your%20lockscreen%2C%20though%20my%20dainty%20thumbs%20had%20to%20strain%20a%20bit%20to%20reach%20it%20one-handed.%20It's%20an%20optical%20fingerprint%20sensor%2C%20so%20it's%20easy%20to%20tell%20how%20far%20off%20you%20are%20if%20your%20scan%20fails%2C%20but%20it%20can%20feel%20blinding%20when%20unlocking%20your%20phone%20at%203%20a.m.%20for%20an%20insomnia%20doomscroll.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Galaxy%20A37%20technically%20comes%20in%20four%20colors%2C%20but%20you%20can't%20find%20all%20of%20them%20in%20one%20place.%20If%20you're%20buying%20at%20your%20carrier%2C%20the%20only%20A37%20you%20get%20is%20Awesome%20Charcoal.%20At%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15126427790pc-20%26h%3D5f5e69bfcca829f39ced249d09c5b84cebb608aa9f2c1bccd62b23f4de597a61%26postID%3D6a04aaa61a1c27f79ffe2538%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftech%252Fsamsung-galaxy-a37-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.samsung.com%252Fus%252Fsmartphones%252Fgalaxy-a37-5g%252Fbuy%252Fgalaxy-a37-5g-128gb-unlocked-sku-sm-a376uzaaxaa%252F%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESamsung%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20most%20unlocked-phone%20retailers%2C%20you%20can%20choose%20between%20Awesome%20Lavender%20and%20Awesome%20Charcoal.%20We%20then%20have%20two%20retailer-exclusive%20colors%3A%20%3Ca%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15126427790pc-20%26h%3D83791fd152a7909ed9274fa36be6ae862fe06ac6cff9cd8df58e5ca2c2a9dc95%26postID%3D6a04aaa61a1c27f79ffe2538%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftech%252Fsamsung-galaxy-a37-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FSamsung-A37-Unlocked-Smartphone-Warranty%252Fdp%252FB0GMKXXTV1%252F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAwesome%20White%20at%20Amazon%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.ins