nce%20we%20are%20judging%20this%20phone%20by.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225a415384-cfeb-4713-9c44-4f8328542f3d%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Performance%5C%22%3EPerformance%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223209%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Samsung%20Galaxy%20A37%20showing%20Google%20Chat%20menu.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a04b5fbecd7cc1332baed69%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222407%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20120Hz%206.7-inch%20display%20is%20rare%20at%20this%20price.%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%2FAra%20Wagoner%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELet's%20start%20with%20the%20obvious%3A%20the%20Galaxy%20A37%20runs%20an%20Exynos%201480%20from%202024%20with%206GB%20of%20RAM%20and%20is%20not%20meant%20for%20gamers%20or%20power-users%20of%20any%20kind.%20While%20this%20is%2C%20on%20paper%2C%20a%20higher-performance%20chipset%20than%20last%20year's%20Snapdragon%206%20Gen%203%2C%20you%20can%20find%20its%20limits%20very%20quickly%2C%20even%20without%20gaming.%20You%20%3Cem%3Ecan%3C%2Fem%3E%20game%20on%20this%20phone%20%E2%80%94%20and%20most%20of%20my%20screen%20time%20with%20this%20phone%20was%20Merge%20Dragons%20and%20Pok%C3%A9mon%20Go%20%E2%80%94%20but%20you're%20going%20to%20have%20to%20fine-tune%20the%20quality%20settings%20into%20oblivion%20and%20then%20some.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhenever%20I%20woke%20my%20phone%20back%20up%20during%20a%20Merge%20Dragons%20event%2C%20the%20game%20hung%20for%20about%205-8%20seconds%20on%20average%2C%20and%20crashed%20while%20idle%20over%20half%20a%20dozen%20times%20in%20a%20single%20weekend.%20Pok%C3%A9mon%20Go%20would%20kick%20me%20back%20to%20the%20Niantic%20load%20screen%20almost%20every%20time%20I%20swapped%20to%20another%20app%2C%20even%20for%20just%20a%20quick%20Instagram%20DM%20reply.%20There%20was%20no%20GPS%20drift%20at%20least%20%E2%80%94%20something%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fgoogle-pixel-10a-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle%20Pixel%2010a%3C%2Fa%3E%20struggled%20with%20%E2%80%94%20but%20lag%20in%20the%20game%20itself%20seemed%20to%20pop%20up%20consistently%20after%20about%20an%20hour%20of%20continuous%20raids%2C%20leading%20to%20several%20missed%20throws%20and%20escapes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20reading%20my%20webtoons%2C%20doomscrolling%20Threads%2C%20or%20bingeing%20YouTube%2C%20the%20A37%20had%20me%20easily%20covered%20so%20long%20as%20I%20was%20only%20switching%20between%202-3%20apps%20at%20a%20time.%20Gemini%20could%20be%20a%20bit%20slow%20at%20times%20when%20processing%20multimedia%20tasks%20like%20image%20creation%20and%20when%20deeper%20into%20research%20topics%2C%20but%20it'd%20only%20be%20noticeable%20next%20to%20a%20flagship.%20You%20do%20feel%20the%20processing%20lag%20during%20fast-paced%20photography%20sessions%20%E2%80%94%20more%20on%20that%20in%20a%20moment%20%E2%80%94%20and%20there%20were%20a%20couple%20of%20times%20when%20the%20phone%20got%20uncomfortably%20warm%20in%20my%20hand%20while%20%3Cstrong%3Enot%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20in%20use%20in%2090-degree%20Florida%20sunshine%2C%20but%20they%20were%20rare%20and%20hard%20to%20reproduce.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223411%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Samsung%20Galaxy%20A37%20nestled%20in%20a%20tree%20branch%20nook%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a04b64c94eb4c909fb2ba88%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222558%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EYou'll%20need%20a%20case%20to%20avoid%20scuffing%20up%20that%20shiny%20rear%20glass.%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%2FAra%20Wagoner%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20most%20budget%20phones%20emphasize%20multi-day%20battery%20life%2C%20Samsung%20completely%20avoids%20battery%20life%20claims%20for%20the%20Galaxy%20A37%2C%20simply%20calling%20the%205%2C000mAh%20battery%20%E2%80%94%20the%20same%20capacity%20this%20series%20has%20used%20since%202020's%20Galaxy%20A31%20%E2%80%94%20%26quot%3Blong%E2%80%94lasting%26quot%3B.%20Unlike%20the%201.5-2%20day%20battery%20life%20we%20see%20on%20competitors%20like%20the%20Google%20Pixel%2010a%20and%20Moto%20G%20Power%202026%2C%20the%20A37's%20is%20strictly%20in%20the%20single-day%20range.%20That%20said%2C%20Samsung%20makes%20up%20for%20it%20with%2045W%20Power%20Delivery%20charging.%20There's%20no%20wireless%20charging%20here%2C%20but%20I'd%20rather%20not%20have%20it%20than%20have%205W%20or%2010W%20charging%20that%20takes%20forever.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMoving%20from%20hardware%20to%20software%20performance%2C%20One%20UI%208.5%20on%20the%20Galaxy%20A37%20puts%20Galaxy%20AI%20%E2%80%94%20Samsung%20should%20be%20ashamed%20for%20calling%20it%20%26quot%3BAwesome%20Intelligence%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20and%20Google%20Gemini%20front%20and%20center%20during%20setup.%20However%2C%20after%20you%20finish%2C%20they%20fade%20into%20the%20background%20almost%20immediately.%20Suggested%20edits%20and%20Object%20Eraser%20in%20the%20Gallery%20app%20can%20be%20useful%20when%20they%20work%20well%2C%20but%20they%20tend%20to%20miss%20as%20much%20as%20they%20hit%20with%20my%20photos.%20Circle%20to%20Search%20remains%20a%20very%20handy%20feature%2C%20but%20it's%20nothing%20new%3B%20the%20A36%20got%20it%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESamsung's%20software%20style%20can%20be%20a%20bit%20of%20an%20acquired%20taste%2C%20especially%20to%20those%20coming%20from%20an%20iPhone%20or%20a%20Pixel%2C%20but%20I've%20found%20the%20slightly%20overstuffed%20toolbox%20of%20One%20UI%20invaluable%20because%20it%20clings%20to%20useful%20older%20features%20that%20other%20manufacturers%20might've%20abandoned%20and%20expansive%20customization%20options%20with%20or%20without%20touching%20the%20Good%20Lock%20ecosystem.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20Google%20Pixel%20devices%20do%20not%20have%20a%20quick%20settings%20menu%20or%20a%20main%20settings%20menu%20for%20sound%2Fvibrate%2Fsilent%20mode%3B%20it's%20only%20accessible%20via%20the%20volume%20rocker.%20Samsung%20One%20UI%20offers%20both%2C%20as%20well%20as%20Temporary%20Mute%2C%20which%20turns%20the%20sound%20back%20on%20after%20a%20preset%20or%20custom%20interval.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223658%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Samsung%20Galaxy%20A37%20screen%20showing%20multiple%20OneUI%20notifications.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a04b0297c7e83f26041b548%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222743%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESamsung's%20on-screen%20notification%20systems%20continue%20to%20embarrass%20Apple's.%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%2FAra%20Wagoner%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESamsung%20Modes%20and%20Routines%20offers%20almost%20double%20the%20premade%20modes%20Google%20does%20%E2%80%94%20including%20a%20Theater%20mode%20that%20keeps%20my%20paired%20Galaxy%20Watch%206%20from%20waking%20up%20as%20I%20gesticulate%20at%20the%20screen%20%E2%80%94%20and%20its%20Apple-mimicking%20Routines%20features%20more%20diverse%20options%20and%20more%20consistent%20performance%20than%20the%20Google%20Assistant%20routines%20you'd%20see%20on%20Pixel%20or%20Motorola%20phones.%20This%20excess%20of%20options%20can%20be%20overwhelming%20at%20times%20and%2C%20admittedly%2C%20clutters%20the%20Settings%20menus%2C%20but%20if%20'better%20to%20have%20it%20and%20not%20need%20it'%20were%20an%20Android%20skin%2C%20it%20would%20be%20One%20UI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20one%20aspect%20of%20One%20UI's%20old%20feature%20hoarding%20that%20crosses%20the%20boundary%20from%20busy-but-useful%20into%20chaos%20theory%20is%20the%20app%20drawer.%20By%20default%2C%20One%20UI%20Home's%20app%20drawer%20is%20a%20paginated%20'custom%20sort'%20that%20adds%20apps%20in%20the%20order%20that%20they%20were%20installed%2C%20with%20pre-installed%20apps%20on%20the%20first%20two%20pages.%20This%20completely%20manual%20app%20drawer%20lets%20users%20customize%20each%20page%20and%20place%20their%20apps%20where%20they%20want%2C%20but%20in%20practice%2C%20it%20just%20dumps%20you%20directly%20from%20the%20setup%20guide%20into%20a%20jumbled%20mess.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cmark%20data-color%3D%5C%22%239efcf6%5C%22%3EIt's%20easy%20enough%20to%20tap%20the%20top-right%20three-dot%20menu%20and%20swap%20to%20alphabetical%20sort%20%E2%80%94%20the%20vertically%20scrolling%20app%20drawer%20that%20we%20see%20on%20almost%20every%20other%20Android%20phone%20and%20third-party%20launcher%20%E2%80%94%20and%20Samsung%20can't%20change%20this%20without%20facing%20a%20mob%20of%20users%20demanding%20to%20put%20their%20apps%20back.%20This%20is%20exactly%20the%20type%20of%20held-over%20feature%20that%20built%20the%20non-nerdy%20half%20of%20Samsung%20die-hards%2C%20but%20it%20would%20be%20nice%20to%20see%20an%20option%20for%20the%20Alphabetical%20app%20drawer%20at%20setup%2C%20maybe%20alongside%20the%20dark%2Flight%20theme%20selection.%3C%2Fmark%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20this%20phone%20launched%20with%20Android%2016%2C%20Samsung%20has%20guaranteed%20it%20will%20receive%20system%20updates%20through%20Android%2022%2C%20as%20well%20as%20six%20years%20of%20security%20updates%2C%20making%20it%20one%20of%20the%20longest%20software%20support%20cycles%20among%20budget%20phones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2220f566ea-e84c-401e-a320-0c6b3850aeac%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Cameras%5C%22%3ECameras%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Composite%20image%20of%20Spaceship%20and%20Earth%20CommuniCore%20Hall%20at%20EPCOT%20Center%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a04b1807c7e83f26041b551%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EExample%20shots%20from%20the%20A37%20shot%20at%20dusk%20and%20night%20at%20EPCOT%20Center.%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%2FAra%20Wagoner%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThings%20haven't%20changed%20much%20in%20this%20department%20this%20year%2C%20even%20with%20a%20slight%20main%20sensor%20bump%20and%20Samsung's%20emphasis%20on%20improved%20Nightography%20mode%2C%20but%20it's%20only%20useful%20if%20you%20can%20stay%20perfectly%20still%20during%20the%202-4%20second%20window.%20Daytime%20photos%20with%20the%20main%20camera%20are%20mostly%20vibrant%20thanks%20to%20Samsung's%20tendency%20to%20oversaturate%2C%20but%20zoom%20photography%20only%20goes%20to%2010x%2C%20and%20the%20detail%20drop-off%20is%20drastic%20after%204x.%20Even%202x%20zoom%20photos%20take%20a%20hit%20on%20sharpness%20and%20detail%20preservation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Composite%20image%20increasingly%20zooming%20closer%20to%20a%20sleeping%20tiger.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a04df4dabc4e9d8857494f1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFrom%20left%20to%20right%3A%201x%2C%202x%2C%20and%204x%20zooms%20of%20the%20Samsung%20Galaxy%20A37's%20main%20camera.%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%2FAra%20Wagoner%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETigers%20Sohni%20and%20Conrad%20expertly%20highlighted%20this%20quality%20step-off%20during%20pre-nap%20constitutionals%20around%20their%20Disney's%20Animal%20Kingdom%20enclosures%2C%20as%20well%20as%20how%20well%20it%20held%20up%20to%20the%20A37's%20biggest%20camera%20competitor%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fgoogle-pixel-10a-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGoogle%20Pixel%2010a%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%2010a's%2048MP%20main%20camera%20only%20goes%20to%208x%20zoom%2C%20so%20it%20couldn't%20get%20quite%20as%20close%20in%20when%20Conrad%20napped%20in%20a%20distant%20gully%2C%20but%20Google's%20processing%20helped%20dial%20in%20the%20details%20on%20the%20tigers%20a%20bit%20better%20than%20Samsung's%2C%20which%20turned%20the%205x-10x%20photos%20into%20watercolors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22blurry%20zoomed-in%20shot%20of%20a%20tiger%20sleeping.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a04dfb094eb4c909fb2bc0e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223060%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20A37's%2010x%20zoom%20loses%20detail%20on%20closer%20subjects%20and%20is%20better%20suited%20to%20wider%20landscape%20shots.%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%2FAra%20Wagoner%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20area%20where%20the%20Galaxy%20A37's%202x%20zoom%20photos%20%E2%80%94%20and%20overall%20photo%20quality%20%E2%80%94%20did%20securely%20triumph%20over%20the%20Pixel%2010a%20was%20during%20evening%20fireworks%2C%20but%20this%20might%20owe%20more%20to%20Samsung's%20camera%20app%20settings%20than%20to%20the%20hardware%20itself.%20While%20the%20Pixel%20has%20split%20its%20brightness%20and%20exposure%20controls%20into%20three%20separate%20sliders%2C%20once%20you%20tap%20on%20your%20area%20of%20focus%2C%20Samsung%20instead%20has%20a%20single%20exposure%20slider%20you%20can%20slide%20up%20and%20down%2C%20then%20lock%20into%20place.%20Samsung%20still%20tends%20to%20overbrighten%20night%20photos%2C%20producing%20grainy%20areas%20without%20a%20direct%20light%20source%2C%20but%20with%20the%20exposure%20slider%2C%20it's%20easy%20to%20yank%20the%20exposure%20down%20a%20bit%20and%20keep%20it%20there%20until%20you%20select%20a%20new%20autofocus%20target.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Fireworks%20at%20EPCOT%20Center%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a04e134ecd7cc1332baef49%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EEPCOT's%20luminous%20fireworks%20show%2C%20photographed%20from%20the%20America%20pavilion%2C%20roughly%20500%20feet%20away.%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%2FAra%20Wagoner%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20result%20is%20that%20I%20spent%20less%20time%20fiddling%20with%20brightness%20and%20could%20focus%20instead%20on%20timing%20my%20shots%20to%20the%20peak%20of%20each%20colorful%20explosion%2C%20which%20became%20a%20rhythm-game%20mini-boss%20of%20its%20own.%20When%20taking%20review%20photos%20of%20fireworks%2C%20I'm%20used%20to%20seeing%20the%20briefest%20of%20pauses%20when%20I%20press%20the%20shutter%20%E2%80%94%20a%20millisecond%20review%20of%20the%20shot%20while%20the%20phone%20processes%20and%20saves%20it%20%E2%80%94%20but%20the%20Galaxy%20A37%20was%20more%20than%20pausing.%20The%20viewfinder%20loitered%20in%20multi-second%2C%20stop-motion%20lag%20for%20about%20half%20the%20show%20as%20the%20limited%20RAM%20and%20older%20processor%20were%20quickly%20overwhelmed%20by%20the%20rapid%20lighting%20changes%20and%20back-to-back-to-back%20shots%20trying%20to%20capture%20as%20much%20pyrotechnics%20as%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20tapping%20the%20shutter%20as%20often%20as%20possible%20during%20each%20volley%2C%20I%20had%20to%20time%20my%20shots%20as%20closely%20as%20possible%2C%20as%20I'd%20be%20lucky%20to%20get%20more%20than%20one%20shot%20off%20during%20the%203-8%20seconds%20between%20each%20boom%20and%20fizzle.%20Mode-swapping%20suffered%2C%20too%2C%20missing%20the%20finale%20in%20the%20lurch%20between%20photo%20and%20video.%20Fireworks%20are%20a%20strenuous%20test%20for%20a%20camera%2C%20but%20it%20shows%20the%20same%20struggle%20you'll%20find%20during%20a%20blindingly%20lit%20stage%20concert%20or%20the%20strobing%20lights%20of%20a%20club.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20indoor%20nature%20display%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a04b21095396a3b6e418069%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223060%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIf%20you%20can%20afford%20to%20take%20time%20with%20stationary%20scenes%2C%20darker%20shots%20can%20look%20great.%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%2FAra%20Wagoner%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20for%20fireworks%2C%20the%20A37%20gets%20a%20nice%20win%2C%20but%20for%20capturing%20human%20forms%20and%20faces%2C%20Samsung's%20left%20out%20one%20of%20the%20best%20features%20for%20group%20photos%20in%20years.%20Best%20Take%20on%20modern%20Pixels%20(aka%20Best%20Face%20on%20recent%20Samsung%20phones)%20selects%20the%20best%20expression%20from%20each%20person%20in%20a%20multi-frame%20photo%20capture%20and%20stitches%20them%20into%20one%20'perfect'%20shot%20with%20AI.%20This%20was%20a%20godsend%20on%20the%20Pixel%2010a%2C%20especially%20for%20selfies%2C%20and%20the%2012MP%20front%20shooter%20on%20the%20A37%20could've%20%3Cem%3Ereally%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20really%20benefited%20from%20some%20extra%20processing%2C%20as%20the%20feature%20didn't%20make%20the%20cut.%20You%20can%20find%20it%20on%20the%20slightly%20pricier%20Galaxy%20A57%2C%20though.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20bright%20daylight%2C%20selfies%20are%20no%20problem%20and%20quality%20is%20perfectly%20passable%20for%20personal%20or%20professional%20video%20calls%2C%20but%20both%20at%20night%20and%20inside%20a%20restaurant%2C%20it%20was%20magnitudes%20harder%20to%20get%20a%20selfie%20that%20was%20both%20in%20focus%20and%20had%20good%20expressions%20on%20both%20subjects%2C%20especially%20with%20my%20weak%20arm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20selfie%20shot%20of%20a%20couple%20in%20front%20of%20the%20large%20tree%20at%20Animal%20Kingdom%2C%20EPCOT%20Center.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a04b2857c7e83f26041b564%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDespite%20the%20omission%20of%20Best%20Face's%20perfect%20shot%20assistance%2C%20daytime%20selfies%20look%20great%20on%20the%20A37.%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%2FAra%20Wagoner%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20A57-only%20upgrade%20was%20the%2012MP%20ultrawide%20camera%2C%20so%20we're%20stuck%20with%20the%20same%208MP%20sensor%20as%20the%20last%20two%20generations%20on%20this%20A37%2C%20meaning%20photos%20are%20noticeably%20dimmer%20and%20less%20vibrant.%20It's%20here%20if%20you%20need%20it%2C%20but%20you'll%20probably%20want%20to%20stick%20with%20the%20main%2050MB%20sensor%20whenever%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlso%20dimmer%20and%20worth%20avoiding%20is%20the%205MP%20macro%20camera.%20Despite%20trying%20multiple%20objects%20of%20varying%20size%2C%20I%20was%20unable%20to%20produce%20a%20single%20macro%20photo%20that%20was%20properly%20in%20focus.%20Samsung%20even%20makes%20it%20easy%20to%20forget%20a%20third%20camera%20exists%2C%20as%20Macro%20mode%20is%20hidden%20in%20the%20More%20submenu%20of%20the%20camera%20mode%20carousel.%20Proper%20macro%20photography%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20more%20flexible%20telephoto%20macro%20%E2%80%94%20remains%20the%20province%20of%20premium%20phones%2C%20but%20if%20it%20matters%20on%20your%20sub-%24500%20phone%2C%20the%20'I'll%20enable%20Macro%20mode%20when%20I%20feel%20like%20it'%20Pixel%2010a%20offers%20less%20control%20but%20better%20quality%20than%20the%20Samsung%20Galaxy%20A37.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20price%20segment%20the%20A37%20sits%20in%2C%20the%20photos%20are%20better%20than%20most%20%E2%80%94%20at%20least%20for%20the%20phones%20we%20get%20here%20in%20the%20US%20%E2%80%94%20and%20if%20the%20processing%20speeds%20weren't%20so%20hampered%20by%20the%20chipset%20it's%20running%20on%2C%20it%20would%20be%20worth%20recommending%2C%20but%20shutterbugs%20should%20look%20to%20either%20the%20Pixel%2010a%20or%20the%20Galaxy%20A57%2C%20which%20features%20an%20upgraded%20ultrawide%20alongside%20the%20newer%20processor%20and%208GB%20of%20RAM.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22136b2042-b052-4ea9-af27-15d9fc54896f%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Should%20you%20buy%20the%20Samsung%20Galaxy%20A37%3F%5C%22%3EShould%20you%20buy%20the%20Samsung%20Galaxy%20A37%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223468%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Samsung%20Galaxy%20A37%20phone%20leaning%20on%20a%20rocky%20wall.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a04b2fb95396a3b6e418080%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222601%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThere's%20a%20lot%20of%20competition%20at%20this%20price%2C%20but%20we've%20seen%20%2475%2B%20discounts%20not%20long%20after%20launch.%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%2FAra%20Wagoner%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20viewed%20next%20to%20its%20big%20brother%2C%20the%20Galaxy%20A57%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15126427790pc-20%26h%3D83791fd152a7909ed9274fa36be6ae862fe06ac6cff9cd8df58e5ca2c2a9dc95%26postID%3D6a04aaa61a1c27f79ffe2538%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftech%252Fsamsung-galaxy-a37-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FSamsung-A37-Unlocked-Smartphone-Warranty%252Fdp%252FB0GMKXXTV1%252F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESamsung%20Galaxy%20A37%3C%2Fa%3E%20comes%20out%20well%20for%20the%20%24100%2B%20you%20save.%20Yes%2C%20the%20A57%20has%208GB%20of%20RAM%20standard%20instead%20of%206GB%20and%20a%202026%20processor%20instead%20of%20a%202024%20model%2C%20but%20neither%20is%20particularly%20well-suited%20for%20gaming%20or%20heavier%20productivity%20apps%2C%20and%20the%20difference%20in%20photo%20quality%20isn't%20quite%20enough%20to%20justify%20the%20price%20difference%20for%20most%20of%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20vacuum%2C%20the%20A37%20can%20justify%20itself%2C%20but%20once%20we%20start%20looking%20at%20the%20other%20phones%20in%20and%20around%20this%20price%20range%2C%20it%20faces%20some%20steep%20competition%20from%20the%20%24499%20(often%20%24449)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fgoogle-pixel-10a-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle%20Pixel%2010a%3C%2Fa%3E.%20First%20and%20foremost%2C%20performance%20is%20significantly%20better%20on%20the%20Pixel%2010a%3B%20I%20watched%20apps%20hang%20and%20games%20crash%20semi-regularly%20on%20the%20A37%2C%20but%20the%20only%20time%20I%20ran%20into%20noticeable%20performance%20issues%20on%20the%20Pixel%2010a%20was%20swapping%20between%20the%20camera%2C%20Pok%C3%A9mon%20Go%2C%20and%20Instagram%20in%20the%20Florida%20heat.%20The%20Pixel%2010a's%20cameras%20%E2%80%94%20or%20perhaps%20the%20AI-processing%20behind%20i