ccess%20to%20clean%2C%20fresh%20water.%20The%20easiest%20way%20to%20provide%20fresh%20water%20is%20with%20one%20of%20the%20best%20cat%20water%20bowls.%20A%20good%20bowl%20will%20be%20made%20from%20high-quality%20materials%20like%20stainless%20steel%20or%20lead-free%20ceramic%2C%20have%20a%20cat-friendly%20design%20that%20prioritizes%20head%20and%20neck%20comfort%2C%20and%20be%20a%20breeze%20to%20fill%20and%20clean.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20a%20pet%20health%20writer%20and%20cat%20parent%20myself.%20At%20almost%208%20years%20old%2C%20my%20tuxedo%20cat%20Stacie%20is%20set%20in%20her%20ways%20and%20has%20a%20sensitive%20stomach%2C%20so%20I%20knew%20she'd%20have%20strong%20opinions%20about%20the%20bowls%20we%20tested%20for%20this%20guide.%20To%20find%20the%20best%20options%2C%20I%20also%20consulted%20two%20veterinarians%20and%20a%20cat%20behaviorist%20and%20researched%20dozens%20of%20products.%20After%20testing%2011%20bowls%2C%20Stacie%20and%20I%20chose%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15126426486mm-20%26h%3D34be8cbe6e9b056f191c851e6db1ca929ca6c8c818c72a5aae6c78e7e4c74ce1%26postID%3D6a0485f7f5bb6697df37e7cb%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fpets%252Fbest-cat-water-bowl%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.chewy.com%252Floving-pets-bella-non-skid-stainless%252Fdp%252F39528%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELoving%20Pets%20Bella%20Bowl%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20the%20best%20overall.%20It's%20budget-friendly%2C%20dishwasher-safe%20for%20convenient%20cleaning%2C%20made%20from%20a%20combination%20of%20durable%20stainless%20steel%20and%20poly-resin%2C%20and%20comes%20in%20many%20fun%20patterns%20and%20colors%20to%20fit%20any%20cat's%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ERead%20more%20about%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fhow-we-test-pet-products%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Ehow%20