ption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20standout%20feature%20is%20the%20nonskid%20rubber%20bottom%2C%20which%20keeps%20slipping%2C%20splashing%2C%20and%20messes%20to%20a%20minimum.%20While%20I%20love%20Stacie's%20long%20fur%2C%20it%20often%20gets%20wet%20when%20she%20drinks%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20mess%20around%20the%20bowl.%20With%20the%20Bella%20Bowl%2C%20the%20splashes%20from%20wet%20fur%20were%20minimal%20due%20to%20its%20wide%20rim.%20Keep%20in%20mind%20that%20while%20the%20bowl%20is%20dishwasher-safe%2C%20you'll%20need%20to%20remove%20the%20rubber%20base%20before%20washing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnlike%20other%20stainless%20steel%20bowls%20I%20tested%2C%20the%20Bella%20Bowl%20comes%20in%20eight%20different%20colors%20and%20patterns.%20If%20all%20of%20that%20isn't%20enough%2C%20it%20was%20also%20Stacie's%20favorite.%20She%20drank%20the%20most%20from%20it%20during%20testing%20and%20continues%20to%20use%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226e204cbe-ba0f-4837-9254-82ba03a0f3b4%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20stainless%20steel%5C%22%3EBest%20stainless%20steel%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EStainless%20steel%20is%20widely%20considered%20one%20of%20the%20best%20materials%20for%20cat%20bowls%20because%20it's%20durable%2C%20hygienic%2C%20and%20easy%20to%20clean.%20Unlike%20plastic%2C%20stainless%20steel%20is%20less%20prone%20to%20bacterial%20and%20biofilm%20growth.%20Biofilm%20is%20a%20collection%20of%20bacteria%20or%20other%20water-resistant%20microbes%20that%20live%20inside%20an%20extracellular%20matrix.%20It's%20thin%2C%20slimy%2C%20often%20invisible%2C%20and%20causes%20a%20slippery%20texture%2C%20says%20Joey%20Lusvardi%2C%20a%20Certified%20Cat%20Behavior%20Consultant%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fclassactcats.com%2Fabout%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EClass%20Act%20Cats%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Additionally%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpmc.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Farticles%2FPMC8076466%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eresearch%20shows%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20tap%20water%20left%20in%20a%20bowl%20for%20more%20than%2012%20hours%20was%20significantly%20more%20contaminated%20than%20treated%20water%20left%20for%20the%20same%20duration.%20The%20same%20study%20also%20shows%20higher%20levels%20of%20E.%20coli%20contamination%20in%20bowls%20of%20long-haired%20cats%20than%20in%20those%20of%20short-haired%20cats.%20All%20of%20this%20to%20say%2C%20a%20stainless%20steel%20bowl%20is%20the%20ideal%20choice%20for%20keeping%20your%20cat's%20water%20more%20free%20of%20harmful%20bacteria%20and%20biofilms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20capacity%20and%20convenience%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15126426486mm-20%26h%3D280cd8e2286205ee854216163bd76a416a6781767fda69aa98b76f5fba755936%26postID%3D6a0485f7f5bb6697df37e7cb%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fpets%252Fbest-cat-water-bowl%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FPEGGY11-Stainless-Premium-Nonslip-Dishwasher%252Fdp%252FB0BDZ8WBG6%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPEGYY11%20Nonslip%20Stainless%20Steel%20Bowls%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20the%20best%20in%20this%20category%20by%20far.%20Each%20bowl%20holds%20about%202%20cups%20of%20water%20and%20comes%20in%20a%202-pack%2C%20so%20you%20can%20switch%20them%20out%20between%20cleanings.%20Like%20my%20other%20top%20picks%2C%20the%20PEGGY11%20bowls%20have%20a%20nonslip%20base.%20The%20ridged%20silicone%20bottom%20is%20perfect%20for%20cats%20like%20Stacie%20who%20take%20big%20gulps%20that%20can%20shake%20the%20bowl.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Side-by-side%20photos%20show%20a%20shallow%20stainless%20steel%20pet%20bowl%20from%20side%20and%20top%20views%20on%20a%20white%20tray.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a04cd0becd7cc1332baee37%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EKathleen%20Frost%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20feature%20I%20liked%20was%20how%20well%20the%20bowls%20held%20up%20to%20daily%20cleaning.%20Stainless%20steel%20rinses%20better%20than%20ceramic%20because%20it's%20nonporous%20and%20lightweight.%20And%20I%20could%20simply%20toss%20the%20bowls%20in%20the%20dishwasher%20without%20worrying%20about%20damage.%20After%20several%20days%2C%20I%20didn't%20see%20the%20slimy%20biofilm%20that%20often%20forms%20around%20the%20edges%20of%20water%20bowls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20bowl's%20materials%20are%20excellent%2C%20it%20only%20comes%20in%20gray%2C%20making%20it%20a%20poor%20choice%20for%20cat%20parents%20who%20want%20a%20pop%20of%20color.%20Additionally%2C%20while%20handwashing%20the%20bowl%2C%20the%20ridged%20bottom%20caused%20water%20to%20splash%20onto%20the%20sink%2C%20my%20hands%2C%20and%20my%20shirt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226f1d5898-70ff-4213-9b42-6850413e72a1%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20raised%5C%22%3EBest%20raised%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EElevated%20water%20bowls%20are%20designed%20to%20bring%20the%20basin%20up%20to%20a%20cat's%20natural%20drinking%20height%2C%20reducing%20neck%20strain%20from%20bending%20down%2C%20says%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fvcahospitals.com%2Ffrench-creek%2Fteam%2Felizabeth-godeke%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDr.%20Elizabeth%20Goedeke%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20medical%20director%20at%20VCA%20French%20Creek%20Animal%20Hospital.%20These%20types%20of%20water%20bowls%20are%20best%20for%20older%20cats%20and%20those%20with%20arthritis%20or%20other%20mobility%20issues.%20Stacie%20was%20familiar%20with%20this%20type%20of%20water%20bowl%20because%20its%20elevation%20and%20design%20are%20similar%20to%20those%20of%20the%20Necoichi%20bowl%20she%20had%20used%20for%20months%20before%20we%20started%20testing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20top%20pick%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15126426486mm-20%26h%3De601369e4beb2806c527a953a5c70e254d575d33afa29eca000a90f3db276c9b%26postID%3D6a0485f7f5bb6697df37e7cb%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fpets%252Fbest-cat-water-bowl%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.chewy.com%252Fnecoichi-ceramic-elevated-cat-water%252Fdp%252F146198%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENecoichi%20Ceramic%20Elevated%20Cat%20Water%20Bowl%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20is%20a%20non-porous%20porcelain%20bowl%20that%20is%20free%20of%20heavy%20metals%2C%20including%20lead%20and%20cadmium%2C%20and%20is%20dishwasher-safe.%20Inside%20the%20bowl%2C%20there%20are%20clear%20measurement%20lines%20that%20make%20it%20easy%20to%20track%20your%20cat's%20water%20intake.%20Lastly%2C%20a%20small%20inner%20lip%20and%20a%20detachable%20silicone%20base%20help%20contain%20water%20and%20prevent%20slipping%20%E2%80%94%20that%20meant%20fewer%20splashes%20on%20the%20floor%2C%20even%20when%20Stacie%20drank%20a%20lot%20of%20water%20at%20once.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Side-by-side%20photos%20show%20a%20white%20ceramic%20cat%20bowl%20with%20paw-print%20details%20and%20interior%20measurement%20markings%20from%20side%20and%20top%20views%20on%20a%20wooden%20table.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a04d21babc4e9d885749452%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EKathleen%20Frost%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20a%20couple%20of%20downsides%20to%20this%20bowl.%20It%20carries%20a%20higher%20price%20tag%20and%20can%20break%20or%20chip%20if%20knocked%20over%20or%20dropped.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20bowl%20has%20a%20slightly%20smaller%20capacity%20and%20a%20narrower%20width.%20%26quot%3BProviding%20relatively%20wide-faced%20water%20bowls%20may%20provide%20benefit%20for%20some%20cats%2C%26quot%3B%20Kornreich%20says.%20However%2C%20he%20debunks%20%26quot%3Bwhisker%20fatigue%26quot%3B%20as%20a%20consideration%20for%20a%20cat's%20water%20bowl.%20While%20whisker%20stress%20has%20been%20noted%20anecdotally%2C%20he%20says%20that%20it's%20a%20hypothetical%20condition%20and%20not%20proven%20in%20a%20%26quot%3Bscientifically%20rigorous%20manner.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a3fe7ac0-a69a-44dd-9ef2-d56587b1bfed%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20ceramic%5C%22%3EBest%20ceramic%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECeramic%20bowls%20are%20a%20popular%20choice%20for%20cats%20because%20they're%20nonporous%2C%20easy%20to%20sanitize%2C%20and%20naturally%20heavier%20than%20plastic%2C%20which%20helps%20prevent%20them%20from%20sliding%20while%20a%20cat%20drinks.%20In%20my%20testing%2C%20the%20standout%20ceramic%20bowl%20was%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15126426486mm-20%26h%3D77a0d3024cd23a2f85328e2b0451ee0aeaaa5469bbd75aad6139d78933cb3505%26postID%3D6a0485f7f5bb6697df37e7cb%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fpets%252Fbest-cat-water-bowl%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.chewy.com%252Fpetrageous-designs-metro-oval-ceramic%252Fdp%252F55201%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPetrageous%20Designs%20Metro%20Oval%20dish%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20holds%20up%20well%20to%20daily%20cleaning.%20Compared%20to%20the%20other%20bowls%20we%20tested%2C%20this%20one%20was%20the%20widest%20and%20lowest%20to%20the%20ground.%20Stacie%20preferred%20drinking%20from%20it%20more%20than%20any%20other%20ceramic%20bowl%2C%20especially%20when%20it%20was%20right%20next%20to%20her%20food%20bowl.%20She%20also%20drank%20from%20it%20frequently%20when%20I%20placed%20it%20in%20the%20second%20location%20near%20our%20spare%20bedroom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Side-by-side%20photos%20show%20a%20shallow%20white%20ceramic%20pet%20bowl%20with%20black%20trim%20and%20paw-print%20designs%20from%20top%20and%20side%20angles%20on%20a%20hardwood%20floor.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a04ddf1ecd7cc1332baeee0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EKathleen%20Frost%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20like%20other%20ceramic%20and%20porcelain%20bowls%2C%20the%20Metro%20Oval%20dish%20is%20prone%20to%20cracking%20or%20breaking%20if%20dropped.%20It%20also%20lacks%20a%20rubber%20or%20silicone%20base%2C%20so%20you're%20more%20likely%20to%20see%20spills%20and%20splashing%20with%20messy%20drinkers%20like%20Stacie.%20And%20while%20the%20bowl%20is%20wide%2C%20its%20capacity%20is%20limited.%20Smaller%20capacity%20bowls%20tend%20to%20get%20dirtier%20faster%2C%20necessitating%20frequent%20refills.%20For%20example%2C%20I%20found%20myself%20topping%20off%20or%20completely%20refilling%20the%20bowl%20at%20least%20twice%20a%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2273518cfe-30c9-4e4b-8050-b4de8eb76c11%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20fountain%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBest%20fountain%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjournals.sagepub.com%2Fdoi%2Ffull%2F10.1177%2F1098612X18803753%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EResearch%20shows%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20type%20of%20water%20bowl%20doesn't%20matter%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20water%20intake%20%E2%80%94%20it%20all%20depends%20on%20what%20your%20cat%20likes.%20If%20your%20cat%20completely%20avoids%20a%20regular%20water%20bowl%2C%20a%20cat%20fountain%20with%20running%20water%20might%20be%20a%20better%20option.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15126426486mm-20%26h%3Dcbc8c2503771d745f1065e180f35938c45785469d1c8acd804c83d2a8bd89e57%26postID%3D6a0485f7f5bb6697df37e7cb%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fpets%252Fbest-cat-water-bowl%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FPETLIBRO-Stainless-Automatic-Dispenser-Adjustable%252Fdp%252FB0GDCZCXMY%252F%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPetlibro%20Stainless%20Steel%20Fountain%3C%2Fa%3E%20landed%20in%20the%20top%20spot%20in%20our%20guide%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fbest-cat-water-fountain%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebest%20cat%20water%20fountains%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It's%20a%20whisper-quiet%20fountain%20that's%20perfect%20for%20cats%20and%20humans%20alike.%20It's%20affordable%2C%20made%20of%20food-grade%2C%20durable%20stainless%20steel%2C%20and%20easy%20to%20clean.%20It%20also%20has%20an%20adjustable%20spout%20with%20two%20flow%20settings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20black-and-white%20cat%20sits%20on%20a%20kitchen%20counter%2C%20looking%20down%20at%20a%20stainless%20steel%20water%20fountain%20plugged%20into%20the%20wall.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69e7c89e3fecbb42897a24c2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221875%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJanelle%20Leeson%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20fountain%20lacks%20a%20backup%20water%20supply%20if%20the%20power%20goes%20out%2C%20which%20is%20why%20you%20should%20always%20provide%20additional%20non-powered%20water%20sources%20throughout%20your%20home.%20Extra%20water%20bowls%20are%20a%20practical%2C%20budget-friendly%20option.%20And%20remember%20that%20fountains%20and%20bowls%20are%20both%20good%20options.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20no%20definite%20scientific%20evidence%20that%20cats%20will%20drink%20more%20from%20a%20water%20fountain%20than%20a%20bowl%2C%26quot%3B%20Kornreich%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2238a65756-156a-4064-9472-4539db086391%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22What%20to%20look%20for%5C%22%3EWhat%20to%20look%20for%20in%20a%20cat%20water%20bowl%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20no%20single%20perfect%20cat%20water%20bowl.%20No%20matter%20which%20bowl%20you%20choose%2C%20Lusvardi%20says%20it%20needs%20to%20be%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ficatcare.org%2Fresources%2Fcat-carer-guide-encouraging-your-cat-to-drink.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eone%20your%20cat%20enjoys%20drinking%20out%20of%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Based%20on%20my%20research%2C%20expert%20insights%2C%20and%20personal%20experience%2C%20here%20are%20the%20key%20features%20to%20consider%20when%20choosing%20the%20right%20bowl%20for%20your%20cat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECat-friendly%20design%20and%20capacity%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20All%20of%20the%20experts%20I%20spoke%20with%20agree%20with%20Kornreich%20that%2C%20while%20empirical%20evidence%20supporting%20whisker%20fatigue%20is%20lacking%2C%20it%20can't%20hurt%20to%20choose%20a%20bowl%20that's%20wider%20to%20prevent%20potential%20sensory%20overload.%20Lusvardi%20says%20a%20cat's%20whiskers%20typically%20span%20a%20few%20inches%20and%20are%20about%20as%20wide%20as%20their%20body.%20This%20width%20helps%20the%20cat%20determine%20if%20they%20can%20fit%20through%20an%20opening.%20Look%20for%20a%20bowl%20slightly%20wider%20than%20your%20cat's%20whiskers%20if%20possible.%20Like%20many%20cats%2C%20Stacie's%20whiskers%20are%20not%20one%20length%2C%20so%20finding%20a%20bowl%20as%20wide%20as%20her%20longest%20whiskers%20was%20crucial.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20height%2C%20Goedeke%20says%20that%20since%20cats%20are%20smaller%20and%20lower%20to%20the%20ground%20than%20dogs%2C%20it's%20generally%20best%20to%20choose%20a%20lower-height%20bowl%20for%20easier%20access.%20However%2C%20she%20says%20elevated%20bowls%20are%20an%20exception%20since%20they%20allow%20cats%20to%20drink%20in%20a%20comfortable%2C%20upright%20position%20with%20their%20neck%20neutral.%20The%20rim%20of%20an%20elevated%20bowl%20should%20align%20roughly%20with%20a%20cat's%20lower%20chest%20or%20elbow%20level%2C%20allowing%20them%20to%20drink%20without%20excessive%20stretching%20or%20bending.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELastly%2C%20a%20cat's%20water%20bowl%20should%20hold%20at%20least%20their%20daily%20water%20intake%20requirement.%20Generally%2C%20Kornreich%20says%20a%2010-pound%20cat%20should%20drink%208%20to%2010%20fluid%20ounces%20of%20water%20a%20day%20if%20they%20are%20on%20a%20dry%20diet%20only.%20Cats%20with%20conditions%20such%20as%20chronic%20kidney%20disease%2C%20diabetes%2C%20urinary%20tract%20disease%2C%20and%20constipation%20may%20need%20to%20drink%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EScratch-proof%2C%20bacteria-resistant%20materials%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Any%20smooth%2C%20nonporous%20material%20is%20ideal.%20Among%20materials%2C%20stainless%20steel%20is%20a%20highly%20durable%20option.%20Most%20importantly%2C%20you'll%20want%20to%20thoroughly%20clean%20any%20bowl%20to%20keep%20biofilms%20and%20the%20harmful%20bacteria%20within%20them%2C%20like%20E.%20coli%2C%20Pseudomonas%2C%20and%20Staphylococcus%2C%20to%20a%20minimum.%20If%20these%20microbes%20go%20unchecked%2C%20they%20can%20contaminate%20your%20cat's%20drinking%20water%20and%20lead%20to%20gastrointestinal%20distress.%20Lastly%2C%20look%20for%20stainless%20steel%20bowls%20that%20are%20free%20of%20dents%20and%20discoloration.%20Crack-resistant%20ceramic%20bowls%20are%20also%20a%20great%20option%20for%20water%20bowls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EStable%2C%20nonslip%20base%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Some%20cats%20naturally%20like%20to%20dip%20their%20paws%20into%20their%20water%20bowl%20or%20splash%20water%20around.%20While%20Stacie%20doesn't%20play%20with%20her%20water%2C%20she%20is%20a%20messy%20drinker%20due%20to%20her%20longer%20fur.%20I%20prioritized%20nonslip%20bowls%20with%20rubber%20bottoms%20to%20prevent%20spills%20and%20water%20from%20splashing%20onto%20the%20floor.%20If%20you're%20shopping%20for%20a%20ceramic%20bowl%2C%20look%20for%20a%20heavier%20option%20that's%20less%20likely%20to%20jostle%20around%2C%20like%20my%20pick%20from%20Necoichi.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EReasonable%20price%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Kornreich%20and%20Goedeke%20recommended%20providing%20more%20than%20one%20water%20bowl%20to%20prevent%20territorial%20disputes%20and%20simplify%20access%20to%20water.%20A%20good%20rule%20of%20thumb%20is%20one%20bowl%20per%20cat%20plus%20an%20additional%20one.%20Low-%20to%20mid-priced%20bowls%20made%20from%20durable%2C%20bacteria-resistant%20materials%20like%20stainless%20steel%20and%20lead-free%20ceramic%20are%20practical%2C%20long-lasting%20options.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226a6d6601-985d-44d0-a92a-20fd12d4c156%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20we%20tested%5C%22%3EHow%20we%20tested%20cat%20water%20bowls%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20evaluate%20the%2011%20water%20bowls%2C%20I%20developed%20a%20series%20of%20tests%20based%20on%20what%20I%20learned%20from%20Lusvardi%2C%20Kornreich%2C%20and%20Goedeke.%20I%20tested%20three%20bowls%20at%20a%20time%20in%20different%20areas%20of%20my%20home.%20I%20placed%20one%20of%20them%20beside%2C%20but%20slightly%20separated%20from%2C%20my%20cat's%20food%20bowl.%20The%20next%20bowl%20was%20positioned%20by%20the%20doorway%20to%20our%20spare%20bedroom%2C%20where%20Stacie%20likes%20to%20sleep%20during%20the%20day.%20The%20third%20bowl%20was%20the%20farthest%20from%20Stacie's%20food%20bowl%2C%20beside%20a%20window%20in%20our%20living%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20tested%20each%20bowl%20for%20an%20average%20of%20three%20to%20four%20days.%20Some%20bowls%20were%20tested%20for%20less%20time%20due%20to%20their%20bulkiness%2C%20messiness%2C%20or%20impracticality%20in%20my%20home%20%E2%80%94%20these%20bowls%20are%20not%20included%20in%20my%20top%20picks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBeneficial%20design%20for%20cats%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Cats%2C%20including%20Stacie%2C%20can%20be%20very%20particular%20about%20what%20they%20drink%20their%20water%20from.%20I%20chose%20wider%20bowls%20to%20help%20reduce%20possible%20whisker%20irritation.%20Many%20of%20the%20bowls%20also%20had%20a%20slight%20elevation%2C%20making%20them%20easier%20for%20cats%20to%20reach.%20While%20Stacie%20drank%2C%20I%20watched%20for%20signs%20of%20neck%20stress%2C%20difficulty%20keeping%20her%20head%20stable%2C%20or%20other%20signs%20of%20pain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHigh-quality%20materials%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ECat%20bowls%20can%20be%20made%20of%20stainless%20steel%2C%20ceramic%2C%20plastic%2C%20and%20even%20silicone.%20All%20the%20experts%20I%20spoke%20with%20said%20stainless%20steel%20and%20lead-free%20ceramic%20are%20the%20best%20because%20they%20are%20more%20durable%20and%20easier%20to%20clean%2C%20so%20I%20mainly%20chose%20bowls%20made%20from%20those%20materials.%20For%20travel%20or%20collapsible%20bowls%2C%20silicone%20is%20better%20than%20plastic%3B%20Kornreich%20says%20plastic%20can%20develop%20scratches%20over%20time%20that%20can%20harbor%20bacteria.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECapacity%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I%20weighed%20each%20bowl%20with%20a%20food%20scale%2C%20then%20subtracted%20that%20weight%20from%20the%20total%20when%20it%20was%20filled%20with%20water%20to%20determine%20its%20capacity.%20To%20track%20how%20much%20Stacie%20drank%2C%20I%20reweighed%20the%20bowls%20at%20the%20end%20of%20each%20day%20using%20the%20same%20method.%20I%20also%20used%20a%20pet%20camera%20to%20monitor%20how%20often%20Stacie%20approached%20each%20bowl.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECleanability%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EKeeping%20your%20cat's%20water%20bowls%20clean%20is%20essential%20to%20prevent%20bacteria%20buildup.%20I%20left%20some%20promising%20bowls%20out%20to%20see%20how%20much%20dirt%20and%20hair%20accumulated%2C%20and%20noted%20which%20bowls%20needed%20more%20frequent%20cleaning.%20I%20washed%20all%20bowls%20by%20hand%20for%20comparison%20and%20evaluated%20whether%20they%20were%20dishwasher-safe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPotential%20for%20spills%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EContrary%20to%20popular%20belief%2C%20some%20cats%2C%20especially%20Bengals%2C%20love%20water%20and%20especially%20enjoy%20playing%20with%20it.%20To%20simulate%20these%20scenarios%2C%20I%20gently%20bumped%20each%20bowl%20after%20I%20filled%20it%20halfway%20to%20see%20how%20much%20water%20would%20splash%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fe684825-dcff-4270-ac79-f8dfd0bc3d2d%5C%22%3EMeet%20the%20expert%20behind%20this%20guide%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKathleen%20Frost%2C%20freelance%20pet%20reporter%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I'm%20a%20freelance%20pet%20reporter%20for%20Business%20Insider%20Reviews%2C%20and%20have%20worked%20as%20a%20health%20writer%20and%20editor%20for%20Rover%2C%20PetMD%2C%20Chewy%2C%20and%20Petco.%20Over%20the%20years%2C%20I've%20interviewed%20dozens%20of%20veterinarians%20and%20behaviorists%20about%20all%20things%20cat%20health%20and%20behavior.%20I%20also%20have%20a%20master's%20degree%20in%20science%20writing%20from%20Johns%20Hopkins%20University.%20I've%20had%20my%20cat%20Stacie%20since%20she%20was%207%20months%20old%2C%20so%20I've%20built%20the%20kind%20of%20trust%20where%20I%20know%20she's%20down%20to%20participate%20in%20any%20testing%20I%20whip%20up.%20I%20knew%20she'd%20be%20the%20perfect%20tester%20for%20all%20of%20these%20water%20bowls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b6977580-4aee-4969-b79c-d827d677f684%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22FAQs%5C%22%3ECat%20water%20bowls%20FAQs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch3%3EWhat%20type%20of%20bowl%20do%20cats%20prefer%20for%20water%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20no%20single%20right%20type%20of%20cat%20water%20bowl.%20While%20our%20experts%20prefer%20wide%2C%20shallow%20bowls%20for%20their%20own%20cats%2C%20raised%20bowls%20might%20be%20better%20for%20older%20cats%20or%20those%20with%20mobility%20issues.%20For%20example%2C%20Lusvardi%20says%20a%20shallow%20bowl%20is%20best%20if%20your%20cat%20likes%20to%20dip%20their%20paws%20into%20the%20water.%20However%2C%20cats%20like%20Stacie%2C%20approaching%20middle%20or%20older%20age%2C%20might%20prefer%20a%20larger%2C%20elevated%20bowl%20so%20they%20don't%20have%20to%20lean%20all%20the%20way%20down%20to%20drink.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EWhat%20material%20is%20best%20for%20a%20cat%20water%20bowl%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EStainless%20steel%20is%20the%20most%20recommended%20material%20for%20cat%20water%20bowls%20because%20it's%20bacteria-resistant%20and%20often%20scratch-resistant.%20A%20lead-free%2C%20BPA-free%2C%20dishwasher-safe%20ceramic%20bowl%20is%20a%20great%20option%2C%20too.%20It's%20best%20to%20avoid%20plastic.%20Lusvardi%20and%20Kornreich%20say%20plastic%20bowls%20are%20a%20breeding%20ground%20for%20bacteria.%20If%20you're%20traveling%2C%20walking%20your%20cat%2C%20or%20need%20one%20on%20the%20go%2C%20a%20silicone%20travel%20bowl%20like%20%3Ca%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15126426486mm-20%26h%3D504e7b9ae4a0b8090286d73d14b83cfeca865ab0d50b9b13505a796c014b59b0%26postID%3D6a0485f7f5bb6697df37e7cb%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fpets%252Fbest-cat-water-bowl%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.chewy.com%252Ffrisco-silicone-collapsible-travel%252Fdp%252F379031%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethis%20Frisco%20one%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20OK%20as%20long%20as%20you%20clean%20it%20thoroughly%20after%20each%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EHow%20often%20should%20you%20clean%20your%20cat's%20water%20bowl%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20experts%20recommend%20washing%20your%20cat's%20water%20bowls%20once%20a%20day.%20Daily%20cleaning%20prevents%20slime%20and%20biofilm%20from%20forming%20around%20the%20edges%20of%20the%20bowl.%20For%20longhaired%20cats%20like%20Stacie%2C%20it%20also%20keeps%20hair%20from%20collecting%20in%20the%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EHow%20many%20water%20bowls%20does%20my%20cat%20need%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20with%20litter%20boxes%2C%20you%20should%20have%20a%20water%20bowl%20for%20each%20cat%2C%20plus%20at%20least%20one%20additional%20bowl%20for%20easier%20access%2C%20especially%20if%20you%20live%20in%20a%20larger%20home.%20This%20helps%20prevent%20territorial%20behavior%2C%20including%20cats%20guarding%20their%20water.%20Goedeke%20also%20recommends%20keeping%20at%20least%20one%20of%20your%20cat's%20water%20bowls%20separated%20from%20their%20food%20bowl%20and%20placing%20them%20in%20quiet%20spots%20to%20limit%20distractions.%20Lastly%2C%20if%20you%20live%20in%20a%20multi-storied%20home%2C%20she%20says%20to%20have%20one%20water%20bowl%20on%20each%20floor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EDo%20cats%20prefer%20warmer%20or%20colder%20water%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ENo%20two%20cats%20are%20the%20same%2C%20so%20it's%20impossible%20to%20say%20which%20temperature%20is%20best.%20A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdergipark.org.tr%2Fen%2Fdownload%2Farticle-file%2F3065278%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2023%20study%3C%2Fa%3E%20evaluating%20a%20small%20group%20of%20cats%20did%20not%20find%20a%20statistically%20significant%20difference%20in%20water%20intake%20between%20cats%20offered%20room-temperature%20water%20or%20water%20cooled%20with%20ice%20cubes.%20To%20learn%20more%20about%20your%20cat's%20preferences%2C%20you%20could%20try%20offering%20a%20bowl%20of%20cold%20water%20alongside%20an%20identical%20bowl%20of%20room-temperature%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3ECan%20cats%20share%20water%20bowls%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20but%20only%20if%20there%20are%20enough%20bowls%20to%20go%20around.%20Kornreich%20says%20cats%20are%20territorial%20animals%20and%20will%20resource%20guard%20if%20there%20isn't%20enough%20water%20to%20go%20around.%20In%20general%2C%20Goedeke%20says%20you%20should%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcatfriendly.com%2Fcat-friendly-homes%2Fwhat-your-cat-needs-to-feel-secure%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emultiple%20water%20bowls%20spaced%3C%2Fa%3E%20around%20your%20home%2C%20especially%20if%20you%20have%20multiple%20cats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EDo%20cats%20prefer%20shallow%20or%20deep%20water%20bowls%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20most%20healthy%20cats%2C%20shallow%20water%20bowls%20are%20best.%20Cats%20are%20low%20to%20the%20ground%2C%20so%20wide%2C%20shallow%20bowls%20make%20it%20easier%20to%20access%20water.%20Additionally%2C%20Kornreich%20says%20because%20a%20cat's%20whiskers%20are%20more%20sensitive%20since%20they're%20embedded%20in%20nerve-filled%20follicles%2C%20the%20larger%20size%20can%20help%20prevent%20possible%20overstimulation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20a%20slightly%20deeper%20water%20bowl%20might%20be%20helpful%20if%20you're%20worried%20your%20cat%20(or%20you)%20might%20make%20a%20mess%20with%20a%20shallower%20bowl.%20For%20example%2C%20I%20found%20I%20preferred%20a%20deeper%20bowl%20because%20the%20shallower%20ones%20were%20messy%20to%20refill%2C%20weigh%2C%20and%20move.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EDo%20certain%20health%20conditions%20affect%20which%20water%20bowl%20is%20best%20for%20your%20cat%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20your%20cat%20has%20certain%20medical%20conditions%2C%20Kornreich%20says%20it's%20best%20to%20work%20with%20a%20vet%20to%20determine%20which%20cat%20water%20bowls%20are%20best%20for%20your%20cat.%20Cats%20with%20these%20conditions%20may%20have%20different%20hydration%20habits%20than%20the%20average%20healthy%20cat.%20Some%20medical%20conditions%20that%20may%20affect%20drinking%20habits%20are%20kidney%20disease%2C%20diabetes%2C%20arthritis%20or%20other%20mobility%20issues%2C%20hyperthyroidism%2C%20dental%20problems%2C%20and%20central%20nervous%20system%20disease.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fbest-cat-water-bowl%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778711192000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a04f42394eb4c909fb2bd50%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fbest-cat-water-bowl%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I%20tested%2011%20cat%20water%20bowls%20and%20asked%20veterinarians%20for%20guidance%20to%20find%20the%20best%20options%20for%20hydration%2C%20hygiene%2C%20and%20comfort.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Kathleen%20Frost%2CJulie%20Liu%2C%20DVM)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Read%20the%20memo%3A%20Cisco%20to%20cut%20about%204%2C000%20jobs%20in%20AI-driven%20restructuring%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223811%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Cisco%20logo%20appears%20in%20an%20image%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a04f245ecd7cc1332baf070%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222541%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECisco%20on%20Wednesday%20announced%20it%20would%20conduct%20layoffs%20affecting%20about%204%2C000%20staff%2C%20or%20under%205%25%20of%20its%20workforce.%3Cp%3EWEF%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ECisco%20plans%20to%20cut%20about%204%2C000%20jobs%20to%20refocus%20on%20AI%2C%20affecting%20less%20than%205%25%20of%20its%20workforce.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EDespite%20layoffs%2C%20Cisco%20sees%20strong%20quarterly%20results%20and%20raises%20sales%20forecast%20on%20AI%20demand.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECisco's%20restructuring%20will%20invest%20more%20in%20AI%20chips%2C%20fiber%20optics%2C%20and%20security%20amid%20job%20cuts.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ECisco%20is%20cutting%20%26quot%3Bfewer%20than%204%2C000%20jobs%26quot%3B%20as%20the%20networking%20giant%20restructures%20its%20business%20to%20focus%20more%20heavily%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flist-companies-replacing-human-employees-with-ai-layoffs-workforce-reductions%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eartificial%20intelligence%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20according%20to%20a%20memo%20from%20CEO%20Chuck%20Robbins%20published%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20layoffs%2C%20which%20affect%20less%20than%205%25%20of%20Cisco's%20workforce%2C%20come%20as%20the%20company%20reported%20stronger-than-expected%20quarterly%20results%20and%20raised%20its%20sales%20forecast%20on%20growing%20demand%20for%20AI%20infrastructure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20regulatory%20filing%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20Cisco%20said%20the%20restructuring%20is%20expected%20to%20cost%20up%20to%20%241%20billion%2C%20largely%20due%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foracle-layoffs-employees-costs-ai-buildout-job-cuts-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eseverance%20expenses%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20company%20said%20it%20expects%20to%20record%20about%20%24450%20million%20of%20those%20charges%20in%20the%20current%20quarter%2C%20with%20the%20remaining%20costs%20carrying%20into%20fiscal%202027.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company's%20stock%20was%20up%20more%20than%2017%25%20in%20after-hours%20trading.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECisco%20joins%20a%20growing%20list%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-is-putting-pure-managers-at-layoff-risk-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etech%20companies%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20have%20tied%20layoffs%20to%20AI-related%20efficiencies%20and%20broader%20organizational%20changes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20memo%2C%20Robbins%20said%20Cisco%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-spending-capex-big-tech-stocks-share-buybacks-market-investing-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eshifting%20investments%3C%2Fa%3E%20toward%20areas%20%26quot%3Bwhere%20demand%20and%20long-term%20value%20creation%20are%20strongest%2C%26quot%3B%20including%20AI%20chips%2C%20fiber%20optics%2C%20and%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20said%20it%20plans%20to%20continue%20hiring%20in%20strategic%20areas%20while%20eliminating%20some%20roles%20as%20part%20of%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-continues-job-cuts-retail-ai-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI-related%20restructuring%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERead%20the%20full%20memo%20below%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Csection%3ETeam%2C%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EToday%20we%20announced%20our%20Q3%20FY26%20earnings%20with%20record%20revenue%20of%20%2415.8%20billion%2C%20up%2012%20percent%20year%20over%20year%2C%20and%20double-digit%20top%20and%20bottom-line%20growth.%20The%20ELT%20and%20I%20could%20not%20be%20prouder%20of%20the%20growth%20you%20have%20all%20delivered%20for%20Cisco.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EThese%20results%20are%20even%20more%20impressive%20given%20the%20complex%20environment%20we're%20operating%20in%20%E2%80%94%20a%20rapidly%20changing%20market%2C%20with%20intensifying%20competition%2C%20and%20a%20global%20shortage%20of%20components%20critical%20to%20support%20our%20portfolio%20and%20the%20AI%20buildout%20from%20our%20customers.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EThe%20companies%20that%20will%20win%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcloudflare-announces-1100-layoffs-amid-ai-focus-shift-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20era%3C%2Fa%3E%20will%20be%20those%20with%20focus%2C%20urgency%2C%20and%20the%20discipline%20to%20continuously%20shift%20investment%20toward%20the%20areas%20where%20demand%20and%20long-term%20value%20creation%20are%20strongest.%20I'm%20confident%20Cisco%20will%20be%20one%20of%20those%20winners.%20This%20means%20making%20hard%20decisions%20%E2%80%94%20about%20where%20we%20invest%2C%20how%20we're%20organized%2C%20and%20how%20our%20cost%20structure%20reflects%20the%20opportunity%20in%20front%20of%20us.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EWith%20this%2C%20we%20are%20making%20changes%20today%20that%20will%20result%20in%20the%20reduction%20of%20our%20overall%20workforce%20in%20Q4%20by%20fewer%20than%204%2C000%20jobs%2C%20representing%20less%20than%205%20percent%20of%20our%20total%20employee%20base.%20Most%20notifications%20will%20begin%20on%20May%2014%20and%20continue%20globally%20in%20alignment%20with%20applicable%20local%20laws%20and%20regulations.%20For%20employees%20whose%20roles%20are%20impacted%2C%20leaders%20will%20share%20details%20directly%20%E2%80%94%20including%20timing%2C%20available%20resources%2C%20support%2C%20and%20benefits%20in%20each%20country.%20This%20will%20include%20pro-rated%20payment%20of%20FY26%20bonuses%20to%20impacted%20employees.%20We%20will%20provide%20support%20in%20finding%20new%20opportunities%2C%20whether%20internal%20or%20external%2C%20through%20Cisco's%20placement%20services%20%E2%80%94%20a%20program%20that%20has%20seen%2075%20percent%20of%20participants%20discover%20their%20next%20role.%20We%20are%20also%20committed%20to%20continued%20personalized%20learning%20and%20will%20provide%20one%20year%20of%20access%20to%20all%20Cisco%20U%20courses%20and%20certifications%2C%20covering%20AI%2C%20Security%2C%20Networking%2C%20and%20more.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EWhile%20we%20are%20reducing%20roles%20in%20some%20areas%2C%20we%20are%20making%20clear%2C%20strategic%20investments%20%E2%80%94%20particularly%20in%20silicon%2C%20optics%2C%20security%2C%20and%20in%20our%20employees'%20use%20of%20AI%20across%20the%20company.%20These%20investments%20are%20building%20from%20a%20position%20of%20strength%20%E2%80%94%20and%20focusing%20on%20the%20technologies%20and%20businesses%20that%20will%20accelerate%20our%20growth%2C%20deliver%20unmatched%20innovation%20to%20customers%20and%20partners%2C%20and%20define%20our%20future.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3ETo%20those%20leaving%20Cisco%2C%20thank%20you%20for%20your%20contribution%2C%20your%20dedication%2C%20and%20the%20mark%20you%20have%20made%20on%20this%20company.%20We%20are%20deeply%20grateful%20and%20are%20committed%20to%20handling%20this%20transition%20with%20the%20care%2C%20clarity%2C%20and%20respect%20that%20defines%20our%20culture.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EFor%20those%20who%20will%20continue%20here%2C%20we%20will%20discuss%20these%20changes%20and%20answer%20questions%20at%20the%20Cisco%20Beat%20on%20May%2021%20at%208%20a.m.%20PT.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EWe%20have%20important%2C%20impactful%2C%20and%20consequential%20work%20ahead.%20Your%20focus%2C%20resilience%2C%20and%20leadership%20are%20vital%20to%20our%20growth%20and%20relevance%20in%20FY27%20and%20beyond.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EChuck%20and%20the%20Executive%20Leadership%20Team%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcisco-announces-4000-layoffs-ai-driven-business-shift-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778710603000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a04f24f94eb4c909fb2bd3e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcisco-announces-4000-layoffs-ai-driven-business-shift-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Cisco%20announced%20job%20cuts%20affecting%20roughly%204%2C000%20staff%2C%20as%20CEO%20Chuck%20Robbins%20shifts%20the%20company's%20focus%20to%20AI%20investments%2C%20buoyed%20by%20strong%20earnings.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ktl%40businessinsider.com%20(Katherine%20Tangalakis-Lippert)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A96%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22By%20day%20a%20priest%2C%20by%20night%20a%20wrestler%3A%20Meet%20the%20Mexican%20hero%20who%20raised%20money%20for%20an%20orphanage%20by%20fighting%20in%20wrestling%20rings%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778710317000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-131077903%2Cimgsize-1648617.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fby-day-a-priest-by-night-a-wrestler-meet-the-mexican-hero-who-raised-money-for-an-orphanage-by-fighting-in-wrestling-rings%2Farticleshow%2F131077904.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F131077904.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fby-day-a-priest-by-night-a-wrestler-meet-the-mexican-hero-who-raised-money-for-an-orphanage-by-fighting-in-wrestling-rings%2Farticleshow%2F131077904.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com