ding%20two%20Bravo%20original%20micro%20dramas%20this%20summer.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHollywood%20is%20leaning%20into%20short-form%20video%20and%20micro%20dramas.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EPeacock%20is%20dipping%20its%20toe%20into%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicro-dramas-reelshort-dramabox-billion-dollar-business-in-us-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emicro%20dramas%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20teaming%20up%20with%20ReelShort%2C%20Business%20Insider%20has%20learned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENBCUniversal%20is%20bringing%2010%20micro%20dramas%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freelshort-taking-on-hollywood-short-dramas-courts-creators-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecategory%20leader%20ReelShort%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20its%20flagship%20streamer's%20mobile%20app%20starting%20on%20Thursday%2C%20two%20people%20familiar%20with%20the%20initiative%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20The%20company%20confirmed%20the%20deal%20but%20didn't%20disclose%20terms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Peacock-ReelShort%20deal%20is%20a%20short-term%20licensing%20arrangement%20that%20will%20precede%20a%20pair%20of%20Bravo%20original%20micro%20dramas%20arriving%20on%20Peacock%20this%20summer%2C%20said%20John%20Jelley%2C%20NBCUniversal's%20SVP%20of%20product%20and%20user%20experience%20for%20Peacock.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20got%20a%20lot%20of%20confidence%20that%20doing%20more%20in%20the%20vertical%20video%20space%20is%20really%20good%20for%20our%20users%20and%20really%20good%20for%20Peacock%2C%26quot%3B%20Jelley%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fveyou-pitch-deck-hollywoods-tommy-harper-launches-micro-drama-app-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMicro%20dramas%20are%20bite-sized%20soap%20operas%3C%2Fa%3E%20known%20for%20their%20cliffhangers%2C%20and%20many%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmini-drama-reelshort-revolution-actor-job-experience-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eromantic-fantasy%20themes%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENBCU%20%26quot%3Bhandpicked%26quot%3B%20the%20ReelShort%20micro%20dramas%20it's%20putting%20on%20Peacock%2C%20Jelley%20said.%20Those%20titles%20include%20%26quot%3BFated%20To%20My%20Forbidden%20Alpha%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BThe%20Call%20Boy%20I%20Met%20In%20Paris%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BBaby%2C%20Just%20Say%20Yes!%26quot%3B%20a%20person%20familiar%20with%20the%20deal%20said.%20ReelShort%2C%20a%20privately%20held%20company%2C%20didn't%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Peacock%20parent%20unveiled%20its%20first%20two%20planned%20micro%20drama%20originals%20from%20Bravo%20this%20week%20at%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fseth-meyers-roasts-david-ellison-paramount-skydance-nbcu-ad-presentation-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eannual%20presentation%20to%20ad%20buyers%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20%26quot%3BCampus%20Confidential%3A%20Miami%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BSalon%20Confessionals%20with%20Madison%20LeCroy.%26quot%3B%20However%2C%20it%20didn't%20announce%20its%20ReelShort%20licensing%20deal%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJelley%20said%20bringing%20ReelShort's%20micro%20dramas%20aboard%20temporarily%20will%20help%20NBCU%20%26quot%3Bmake%20sure%20that%20this%20new%20format%20%E2%80%94%20like%20all%20of%20our%20new%20formats%20that%20we're%20testing%20%E2%80%94%20really%20resonates%20with%20fans.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20lot%20of%20differences%2C%20subtle%20differences%2C%20between%20these%20different%20types%20of%20vertical%20video%20%E2%80%94%20how%20people%20click%20through%2C%20how%20long%20they%20stay%2C%20how%20they%20navigate%20%E2%80%94%20and%20we%20want%20to%20really%20understand%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Jelley%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHollywood%20has%20become%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflix-disney-short-form-video-youtube-tiktok-hol