%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EOpenAI%20exec%20Joshua%20Achiam%20testified%20about%20a%20%26quot%3Btense%20exchange%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20with%20Elon%20Musk%20in%202018.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMusk%2C%20Achiam%20told%20the%20jury%20in%20the%20Musk%20v.%20Altman%20trial%2C%20called%20him%20a%20%26quot%3Bjackass.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20two%20clashed%20over%20AI%20safety%2C%20and%20Achiam's%20colleagues%20later%20gifted%20him%20a%20gold%20%26quot%3Bjackass%26quot%3B%20trophy.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20OpenAI%20executive%20told%20a%20federal%20jury%20Wednesday%20how%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-sam-altman-openai-trial-testimony-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk%3C%2Fa%3E%20once%20called%20him%20a%20%26quot%3Bjackass%26quot%3B%20during%20a%20heated%20clash%20over%20AI%20safety.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJoshua%20Achiam%2C%20OpenAI's%20chief%20futurist%2C%20recalled%20the%20%26quot%3Bpretty%20tense%20exchange%26quot%3B%20during%20testimony%20in%20the%20California%20civil%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-takes-sam-altman-credibility-to-court-openai-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etrial%20between%20Musk%20and%20OpenAI%20CEO%20Sam%20Altman%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20snapped%20and%20called%20me%20a%20jackass%2C%26quot%3B%20Achiam%20testified.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAchiam%20said%20that%20around%2050%20to%2060%20employees%20had%20gathered%20during%20a%20February%202018%20company%20all-hands%20meeting%20for%20a%20question-and-answer%20session%20ahead%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-trial-greg-brockman-testimony-elon-musk-breakup-compute-costs-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMusk's%20planned%20departure%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20startup%20he%20cofounded%20with%20Altman.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Achiam%2C%20then%20a%20research%20scientist%20at%20OpenAI%2C%20Musk%20said%20he%20was%20leaving%20because%20Tesla%2C%20Musk's%20electric%20car%20company%2C%20would%20soon%20compete%20with%20OpenAI%20for%20elite%20AI%20talent%2C%20creating%20a%20%26quot%3Bconflict%20of%20interest.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20also%20indicated%20a%20general%20lack%20of%20confidence%20in%20OpenAI's%20overall%20path%2C%26quot%3B%20Achiam%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20Musk%20%26quot%3Bwanted%20to%20go%20and%20do%20his%20own%20thing%20and%20sort%20of%20pursue%20AGI%20in%20his%20own%20way.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20sounded%20like%20he%20wanted%20to%20race%20towards%20AGI%2C%20like%20he%20wanted%20to%20build%20it%20very%20fast%2C%20because%20he%20was%20very%20worried%20that%20someone%20else%2C%20if%20they%20got%20it%2C%20would%20do%20the%20wrong%20thing%20with%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Achiam%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAchiam%20said%20he%20and%20a%20few%20others%20were%20concerned%20that%20racing%20toward%20AGI%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bfairly%20unsafe%20proposition%2C%26quot%3B%20telling%20the%20jury%20that%20Musk%20was%20proposing%20something%20that%20seemed%20%26quot%3Breckless.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20didn't%20know%20whether%20a%20science%20fiction%20super%20intelligence%20bootstrapping%20event%20where%20you%20set%20the%20thing%20running%20one%20night%2C%20and%20you%20come%20back%20the%20next%20morning%2C%20and%20it's%20so%20unbelievably%20smart%20it%20can%20crack%20encryption%20and%20take%20over%20the%20world%20was%20a%20science%20fiction%20scenario%20or%20not%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-takes-sam-altman-credibility-to-court-openai-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMusk%20has%20accused%20Altman%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20OpenAI%20of%20stealing%20the%20%26quot%3Bcharity%26quot%3B%20they%20cofounded%20together%20in%202015%20through%20its%20shift%20to%20a%20for-profit%20structure%2C%20while%20Altman%20has%20argued%20that%20Musk's%20lawsuit%20was%20driven%20by%20a%20desire%20to%20take%20down%20an%20AI%20competitor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20testimony%20from%20Achiman%2C%20called%20to%20the%20stand%20by%20Altman%20and%20OpenAI's%20lawyers%2C%20appeared%20aimed%20at%20undercutting%20Musk's%20portrayal%20of%20himself%20as%20focused%20on%20AI%20safety%20concerns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20an%20OpenAI%20lawyer%20asked%20whether%20Musk%20may%20have%20been%20trying%20to%20push%20him%20out%20of%20his%20%26quot%3Bcomfort%20zone%26quot%3B%20by%20calling%20him%20a%20jackass%20%E2%80%94%20as%20Musk%20has%20alluded%20to%20in%20his%20own%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-testimony-openai-trial-inside-courthouse-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eprevious%20testimony%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20case%20%E2%80%94%20Achiam%20said%20no.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20that%20was%20why%20he%20called%20me%20that.%20I%20think%20he%20was%20just%20upset%20that%20he%20had%20been%20challenged%2C%26quot%3B%20Achiam%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20meeting%2C%20Achiam%20told%20the%20jury%20that%20a%20few%20colleagues%20expressed%20their%20gratitude%20to%20him.%20At%20the%20next%20company%20all-hands%2C%20he%20was%20presented%20with%20a%20trophy%20%26quot%3Bto%20commemorate%20the%20exchange%2C%20and%20in%20thanks%20for%20having%20stood%20up%20to%20Elon.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20trophy%2C%20Achiam%20said%2C%20was%20a%20gold%20statue%20depicting%20a%20%26quot%3Bjackass%26quot%3B%20with%20an%20inscription%3A%20%26quot%3BNever%20stop%20being%20a%20jackass%20for%20safety.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-executive-recalls-elon-musk-calling-him-a-jackass-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778699392000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a04c0b5ecd7cc1332baedb2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F