%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fad-banner-1756106894.jpg%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fa%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20not%20nostalgia%20driving%20this%20change%2C%20but%20necessity.%20Rising%20childhood%20obesity%2C%20allergies%2C%20and%20attention%20issues%20are%20nudging%20parents%20to%20rethink%20food.%20Nutritionists%20are%20urging%20families%20to%20revive%20traditional%20superfoods%2C%20not%20as%20a%20trend%2C%20but%20as%20everyday%20essentials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20why%20are%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F478326%2Fpalak-arora-millium-millet-startup-ready-to-eat-mixes-ready-to-cook-supporting-local-farmers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20millets%20and%20microgreens%3C%2Fa%3E%20being%20hailed%20as%20game-changers%3F%20And%20how%20can%20today%E2%80%99s%20busy%20parents%20weave%20them%20into%20their%20children%E2%80%99s%20diets%20without%20mealtime%20battles%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMicrogreens%3A%20Tiny%20greens%2C%20big%20impact%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20many%2C%20microgreens%20still%20conjure%20images%20of%20fancy%20restaurant%20plates.%20But%20step%20into%20a%20growing%20number%20of%20Indian%20homes%2C%20and%20you%E2%80%99ll%20find%20trays%20of%20mustard%2C%20radish%2C%20or%20sunflower%20microgreens%20perched%20on%20balconies.%20Within%2010%20to%2012%20days%20of%20planting%2C%20they%E2%80%99re%20ready%20to%20harvest%20with%20their%20tiny%2C%20tender%20shoots%20bursting%20with%20nutrition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fmicrogreens_11zon-1756194438.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5CnBusy%20parents%20can%20easily%20incorporate%20microgreens%20in%20their%20child's%20diet.%5C%22%20